Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,米高梅电影公司出品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,菲律宾浴血战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}主　要　演  员\NRobert Montgomery　罗伯特·蒙哥马利\NJohn Wayne　约翰·韦恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}本片基于约翰·布尔克利和罗伯特·凯利的真实\N英雄事迹改编，影片细致描画了菲律宾保卫战\N中美国鱼雷快艇在41年12月到42年4月间的战斗.\N中尉巴尔克利因此被授予荣誉奖章。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}威廉·怀特将此故事写成了小说，\N而编剧弗兰克·威德将之改编成了剧本，\N影片曾获第18届奥斯卡录音、特技效果奖提名。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:01:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}珍珠港事件发生不久,日军进攻菲律宾.\N驻菲律宾的美军某鱼雷快艇中队不得不\N与占绝对优势的日本舰队展开苦战。\N本片清楚体现了艇员的决心和勇气。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}兹向为本片拍摄作出巨大帮助的美国海军,\N美国陆军,美国海岸警卫队以及战略规划处\N(注:CIA的前身)致以最诚挚的谢意.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H007FFF&}"今天,所有的枪炮停止了吼叫.人类史上\N巨大的悲剧终于结束.我们终于迎来了\N伟大的胜利...                                    .\N这是那千万名为了今日的胜利而捐躯,\N长眠于菲律宾的丛林中及静卧于太平洋\N深处的将士们的心声."                        .\N麦克 阿瑟 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,菲律宾马尼拉湾    1941年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意!各艇注意!\N{\fs14}All boats from Brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,保持队形.他们还都没见过鱼雷快艇呢.\N{\fs14}Make them look good. It's the first time they've seen PT boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意!\N{\fs14}All boats from Brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意!继续保持队形.\N{\fs14}All boats from Brick. Nice going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克,我是拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Brick from Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候表演一下了.\N{\fs14}That ought to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们开的真棒,长官.\N{\fs14}They maneuver beautifully, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-真是一群意气风发的小伙子. -谢谢,长官.\N{\fs14}- A splendid-looking lot of men. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们,我们迟到了.\N{\fs14}Gentlemen, we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的鱼雷艇开的真的很棒.\N{\fs14}Those boats of yours maneuver beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这玩意用来打仗恐怕还是单薄了点.\N{\fs14}But in wartime, I'm afraid I prefer something more substantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,估计很难会有人相信...\N{\fs14}It's wonderful the way people believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,呃,你们的那些火力强大的舢板.\N{\fs14}...in those high-powered canoes of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌,难道你不相信它们吗?\N{\fs14}Don't you believe in them, Rusty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我还信你那些什么 "我可以亲自指挥.."的废话呢.\N{\fs14}And I let you sell me that stuff about a "command of my own. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你指挥34号艇呢,不是吗?\N{\fs14}You skipper the 34 boat, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我还指挥过浴缸里的肥皂呢!\N{\fs14}I used to skipper a cake of soap in a bathtub too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,检阅完毕.\N{\fs14}Secure from inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,解散!\N{\fs14}Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-你们今天表现真不错. -谢谢.\N{\fs14}- Nice show today, fellas. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉?\N{\fs14}Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好.\N{\fs14}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,认识一下,鱼雷艇艇长 索悌·隆格, 拉弗悌·艾肯....\N{\fs14}I'd like you to meet some boat skippers. Shorty Long, Lefty Aiken...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,别走啊?\N{\fs14}What the-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我来介绍,安迪·安德鲁斯. 他刚来这报到.这是索悌·隆格.\N{\fs14}I want you to meet Andy Andrews. He just reported. Shorty Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-很高兴认识你. -谢谢.\N{\fs14}- Happy to know you. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是拉弗悌·艾肯.\N{\fs14}Lefty Aiken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌在哪?\N{\fs14}Where's Rusty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大概在准备报告吧.\N{\fs14}Looks like he's doing his paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-安迪! -嗨,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}- Andy! - Hello, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拉弗悌说你刚报到,怎么样?\N{\fs14}Lefty said you'd checked in. What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啤酒.\N{\fs14}Beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在算所得税吗?\N{\fs14}Figuring your income tax?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是.我一定要想出充足的理由\N{\fs14}No. I had to work out a smooth line...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说服舰队司令让我去驱逐舰.\N{\fs14}...to convince the admiral I belong on a destroyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说你是真的不想在这呆了?\N{\fs14}So you're really quitting the squadron?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,开这种木头玩意可没前途.\N{\fs14}Can't build a Navy reputation riding a plywood dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么想的? 是打算为自己出名...\N{\fs14}What are you aiming at? Building a reputation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还是...为团队想想?\N{\fs14}...or playing for the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,布里克,这么多年,你给了不少慈父般的建议.\N{\fs14}Look, Brick, for years I've been taking your fatherly advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但从来没有什么好主意.\N{\fs14}It's never been very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起,我要独立了.\N{\fs14}From here on in, I'm a one-man band!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那好,我会把你的申请向上呈交的.\N{\fs14}Send in your request. I'll forward it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来杯啤酒?\N{\fs14}How about a beer, Rusty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,5杯生力啤酒.\N{\fs14}Five San Miguels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这音乐不错.\N{\fs14}Nice music.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,三宝颜的猴子没有尾巴\N{\fs14}Oh the monkeys have No tails in Zamboanga
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,三宝颜的猴子没有尾巴\N{\fs14}Oh the monkeys have No tails in Zamboanga
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,三宝颜的猴子没有尾巴\N{\fs14}Oh the monkeys have no tails
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的尾巴被鲸咬掉了.\N{\fs14}They were bitten off by whales
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,三宝颜的猴子没有尾巴\N{\fs14}Oh the monkeys have No tails in Zamboanga
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他再也不会回苏比克湾了\N{\fs14}Oh he won't go back to Subic anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦他再也不会回苏比克湾了\N{\fs14}Oh he won't go back to Subic anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,我们要升起帆去追赶她\N{\fs14}Oh we'll hoist the jib and spank her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们齐声喊"一二,起锚!"\N{\fs14}And we'll pipe, "All hands, up anchor!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是它再也不会回苏比克湾了.\N{\fs14}But he won't go back to Subic anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运儿!\N{\fs14}Lucky dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}[small beer: 也指小人物]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,淡啤酒,淡啤酒,很淡的啤酒.\N{\fs14}Small beer! Small beer! Very small beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,牛奶!沙士汽水!沙士汽水!\N{\fs14}Milk! Sarsaparilla! Sarsaparilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,姜汁汽水!\N{\fs14}Ginger ale!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,油漆以及红辣椒!\N{\fs14}Paint varnish and dash of red peppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们!\N{\fs14}Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请肃静!\N{\fs14}I want absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这两位有话说.\N{\fs14}Boats here has a little speech to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是来发表演讲的,\N{\fs14}I'm not going to make a speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只说点事.\N{\fs14}Just got something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我们的老朋友- 我们的军医就要离开我们了.\N{\fs14}Tomorrow our old pal Doc here is going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在海军干了30年,他退休了.\N{\fs14}He's being paid off after 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中的很多人可能在弄明白 在海军中呆30年意味着什么之前,\N{\fs14}I know most of you kids got a ways to go before you find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就已经离开了海军.我告诉你们,\N{\fs14}...what 30 years in the Navy means.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是奉献!\N{\fs14}It means service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,30年来,经历了战争与和平年代的\N{\fs14}Tough and good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,艰苦的奉献.\N{\fs14}It means serving your country in peace and in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们举杯...\N{\fs14}So let's raise-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在广播重要声明\N{\fs14}We interrupt this program for an important announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早晨,珍珠港平静的周末被雷电打破..\N{\fs14}This morning, the Sunday calm of Pearl Harbor was broken by the thunder-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个时刻让我们一起举杯\N{\fs14}So let's raise our glasses and drink to Doc...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,向受人尊敬的医生\N{\fs14}...with all the solemnity that this occasion demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,致敬.\N{\fs14}To Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打断大家\N{\fs14}Sorry to have to interrupt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fs14}Ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要宣布一个重要的声明\N{\fs14}I have a very important announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,官方的正式声明.\N{\fs14}This is official.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小日本今晨袭击了珍珠港.\N{\fs14}The Japanese have attacked Pearl Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,目前我们就知道这么多.\N{\fs14}There are no details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,全体陆海军人员立即前往驻地报到.\N{\fs14}All Army and Navy personnel must report to their posts immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍:\N{\fs14}I repeat:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,全体陆海军人员立即前往驻地报到.\N{\fs14}All Army and Navy personnel must report to their posts immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌,走吧.\N{\fs14}Let's go, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,你落了东西了.\N{\fs14}Didn't you forget something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这片土地,我父亲长眠与此,\N{\fs14}Land where my fathers died
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这片土地,朝圣者的骄傲,\N{\fs14}Land of the pilgrims' pride
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在山间的每个角落\N{\fs14}From every mountainside
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,让自由之声响遍.\N{\fs14}Let freedom ring
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下.\N{\fs14}Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也不知道.我只是按命令办.\N{\fs14}I don't know. I'm just doing what I'm told. You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,惠特尼,有什么小道消息吗?\N{\fs14}Any hot dope, Whitey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有,布里克.\N{\fs14}Nothing yet, Brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那里可能是日本人要进攻的地方.\N{\fs14}That's probably where they'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请继续.\N{\fs14}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会竭尽全力的,长官.\N{\fs14}We'll do our best, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,刚收到的,长官.\N{\fs14}This just came in, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们,\N{\fs14}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可能已猜到...\N{\fs14}You may assume that a state of war exists between...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,合众国与日本已经处于交战状态.\N{\fs14}...the United States and the Empire of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要保持见机行事.\N{\fs14}Govern yourselves accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了,各位.\N{\fs14}My compliments, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令.\N{\fs14}Here are the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,霍里.\N{\fs14}Hooley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有任务吗?\N{\fs14}Got anything for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那个部分的?\N{\fs14}What do you call that outfit again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷艇3中队.\N{\fs14}Motor Torpedo Boat Squadron Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有呢.或许明天就有了.\N{\fs14}No orders for you now. Maybe tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我们怎么办,坐着傻等吗?\N{\fs14}What do you want us to do? Sit on our duffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我去问下老头子,你等会.\N{\fs14}I'll ask the old man. Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,派一艘艇巡逻,另派一艘待命.\N{\fs14}Have one boat patrol the bay and one stand by for messenger duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,全部快艇已加油完毕. 鱼雷在半小时内完成装填.\N{\fs14}All boats fueled. Torpedoes will be loaded within a half-hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么消息?\N{\fs14}Any dope?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,要我们待命.\N{\fs14}Our orders are to stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那些驱逐舰可没闲着.\N{\fs14}Those destroyers aren't standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们象比赛似的沉在航道上.\N{\fs14}They went down that channel like a rat race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是有命令要他们那么做吧.\N{\fs14}Somebody might have given them orders to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,给你发了20艇12.7mm机枪.\N{\fs14}You got 20 boxes of 50-caliber there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,##给拉弗悌 12艇.\N{\fs14}Give 12 to Lefty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意:\N{\fs14}Now hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不明飞机正接近甲米地.\N{\fs14}Unidentified aircraft approaches Cavite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不明飞机正接近甲米地.\N{\fs14}Unidentified aircraft approaching Cavite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是日本人的.\N{\fs14}Those are Jap planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,朝这来了.\N{\fs14}Headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所有鱼雷艇立即出港.\N{\fs14}All boats out in the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来,等待信号.\N{\fs14}Follow me, and stand by for signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是演习吗?\N{\fs14}Is that another drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不是演习.\N{\fs14}Can't be a drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们加入海军,天天就是训练,训练.\N{\fs14}All we get in this Navy is drill, drill, drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,紧急出动.\N{\fs14}Fire in the paint locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敌机成一字队形.\N{\fs14}One formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,敌机散开了.\N{\fs14}Breaking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,朝我们来了,长官.\N{\fs14}Heading up our way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,准备散开.\N{\fs14}Stand by to disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意, 各艇注意.\N{\fs14}All boats from 41. All boats from 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,准备散开.\N{\fs14}Stand by for scatter plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,装备散开.\N{\fs14}Stand by for scatter plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,斯莫基,\N{\fs14}Thank them, Smokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,按B方案散开.\N{\fs14}Scatter plan Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,按B方案散开.\N{\fs14}Scatter plan Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,散开!\N{\fs14}Execute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,散开!\N{\fs14}Execute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮,斯莫基.\N{\fs14}Good shooting, Smokey. Recognize him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,打的就是他.\N{\fs14}Iknew him well. Shaved his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子,干掉他.\N{\fs14}Get him, Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意.\N{\fs14}All boats from 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,各艇注意.\N{\fs14}All boats from 41.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,返回基地.\N{\fs14}Return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,返回基地.\N{\fs14}Return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很坚固吧？\N{\fs14}Pretty rugged, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Let's go, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,我们都检查过了.仓库被摧毁了.\N{\fs14}We've checked everything, sir. The storeroom's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷没有了,发动机没有了; 备件没有了,什么都没有了.\N{\fs14}No torpedoes, no motors, no spare parts, no nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道科雷吉多尔岛那有没有鱼雷.\N{\fs14}Wonder if they have any torpedoes at Corregidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对啊. - 我去找找看.\N{\fs14}- Might be. - I'll check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨.\N{\fs14}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.29,0:22:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有点糟吧.\N{\fs14}A little rugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么你衣服湿了吗?\N{\fs14}You got wet clothes on underneath that blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不,长官.只是有点害怕.\N{\fs14}Just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊,你还没学会克服它.\N{\fs14}You haven't got a monopoly on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看什么,厨师?\N{\fs14}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看亚利桑那号驶进港的情景...\N{\fs14}Just looking for the Arizona to come steaming up to base...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.32,0:22:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那光亮闪闪的380毫米大炮...\N{\fs14}...with her 14-inch guns blazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,海军舰艇里最好的厨房.\N{\fs14}...and the best cook stoves in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,亚利桑那号?\N{\fs14}Arizona?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,亚利桑那号.\N{\fs14}Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,陆军的人说一支日本特遣舰队正朝林加延湾驶来.\N{\fs14}Some Army boys told us a Jap task force is headed for Lingayen Gulf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 侦察机在黄昏时发现的. - 肯定是要登陆.\N{\fs14}- Planes spotted it at sunset. - Must be another landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,林加延湾\N{\fs14}Lingayen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,医生,给我剪刀.\N{\fs14}Give me those scissors, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-离这只有约200英里.\N{\fs14}That's only about 200 miles from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是235英里.\N{\fs14}Two thirty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛不把他们干到海底去?\N{\fs14}Why don't we knock those babies off?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么打?就凭几条鱼雷艇吗? 把铅笔给我.\N{\fs14}What with? A cake of soap and a bathtub? Give me that pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷先生,舰队司令要你立刻去见他.\N{\fs14}Mr. Brickley, the admiral, sir. Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,检查一下油料.\N{\fs14}Check your gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样,心情是不是好点了?\N{\fs14}Feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你来指挥.\N{\fs14}Take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来吧,检查舰艇, 准备出海.\N{\fs14}Line up your engines, check all boats. Step on it, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大家出动.\N{\fs14}Fire in the paint locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-长官? -布里克雷.\N{\fs14}- Yes? - Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.84,0:23:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,布里克雷来了.\N{\fs14}Mr. Brickley, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官,你找我?\N{\fs14}You sent for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呃,你准备一艘船把我的参谋部 转移到科雷吉多尔岛去.\N{\fs14}Yes, get a boat ready to move my staff to Corregidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的任务是在马尼拉和岛之间传送讯息.\N{\fs14}You'll run messenger trips between Manila and The Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去和参谋长安排一下.\N{\fs14}Work out a schedule with the Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.63,0:24:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,甲米地基地已经失陷了.\N{\fs14}Cavite is finished as a base.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的部队转移到巴丹的西西曼湾湾.\N{\fs14}Move your outfit to Sisiman Cove on Bataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.14,0:24:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么些吗,长官.\N{\fs14}Is that all, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些.\N{\fs14}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.55,0:24:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听说一只日军特遣舰队正朝 林加延湾驶来,是真的吗?\N{\fs14}Is it true that a Jap task force is moving into Lingayen Gulf, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.22,0:24:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把它发送出去吧.\N{\fs14}Type that and send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷,你过来坐.\N{\fs14}Sit down, Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.50,0:24:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,特遣舰队将会登陆.\N{\fs14}That task force will land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.10,0:25:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都无法阻止的.\N{\fs14}You and I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.87,0:25:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如同西班牙的无敌舰队的遭遇, 珍珠港的袭击是场巨大的灾难,\N{\fs14}Pearl Harbor was a disaster, like the Spanish Armada.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.35,0:25:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说,孩子...\N{\fs14}Listen, son...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...比如,我们是职业运动员.\N{\fs14}...you and I are professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.08,0:25:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果老板说"牺牲", 我们就来个牺牲触击...\N{\fs14}If the manager says, "Sacrifice," we lay down a bunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...让别人去跑出全垒打吧.\N{\fs14}...and let somebody else hit the home runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.39,0:25:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道那些退役了的驱逐舰\N{\fs14}We know about those destroyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.39,0:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都停在圣地亚哥港.\N{\fs14}...out of commission, tied up around San Diego.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.90,0:25:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本可以在这用上他们...\N{\fs14}We could use them here...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们不在这儿...\N{\fs14}...but they're not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也不会在这了...\N{\fs14}They won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.87,0:25:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在就是我们为国捐躯的时刻了..\N{\fs14}Our job is to lay down that sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.04,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们长久以来训练为的就是这个..\N{\fs14}That's what we were trained for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.78,0:25:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的职责.\N{\fs14}That's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.75,0:25:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗?\N{\fs14}Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.13,0:25:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.14,0:26:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,都准备好了.\N{\fs14}All set, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.37,0:26:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不出动了.\N{\fs14}Secure your boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.11,0:26:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不出动了?\N{\fs14}Secure the boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.04,0:26:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,索悌,你把将军和他的参谋送到岛上去.\N{\fs14}Shorty, take the admiral and his staff to Corregidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.11,0:26:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拉弗悌,你每天早上9点传送讯息.\N{\fs14}Lefty, you stand by to run a messenger trip daily at 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.72,0:26:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人,把艇带到西斯曼湾去.\N{\fs14}The rest of you take your boats to Sisiman Cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.52,0:26:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和我们呆在这. - 是,长官.\N{\fs14}You join us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.40,0:26:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克,你不是开玩笑吧?\N{\fs14}Are you kidding, Brick?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.21,0:26:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么理由,他们只需要去..\N{\fs14}Theirs not to reason why, theirs but to do-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.91,0:26:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,去死.\N{\fs14}And die.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.31,0:26:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想当烦死人的信差.\N{\fs14}I don't want to be bored to death running messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.05,0:26:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会有兴趣的.\N{\fs14}I'll see that you get the more intriguing ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.15,0:26:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这样有用吗? - 当然有.\N{\fs14}Does that help?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.94,0:28:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有吃的吗,布里克?\N{\fs14}Any chow, Brick?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.61,0:28:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 刀片和牙膏. - 真是上好的食物.\N{\fs14}- Razor blades and toothpaste. - That's a swell diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.95,0:28:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 头,有什么消息吗? - 日军运输船在北边登陆了.\N{\fs14}- What's the dope, Skipper? - Jap transports landed up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.92,0:28:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正修理巴丹呢.\N{\fs14}They're giving Bataan the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.76,0:28:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 早上好,长官.有消息吗? - 没有.\N{\fs14}- Good morning, sir. Any dope? - No dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好,长官.\N{\fs14}Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.97,0:28:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,刚收到的消息.\N{\fs14}A message just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.40,0:28:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱克 威尔将军要立刻见你. 十万火急.\N{\fs14}And Admiral Blackwell wishes to see you immediately. Very urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.27,0:28:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.84,0:28:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是要我们去给加西亚送信.\N{\fs14}Probably wants us to carry a message to Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.81,0:29:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛斯,在41号艇待命.\N{\fs14}Cross, stand by with that 41 boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.48,0:29:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们先去试试刀片.\N{\fs14}Let's use those razor blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.55,0:29:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,厨子,我要你保证清洁的卫生环境.\N{\fs14}Chief, I want you to keep sanitary precautions at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.22,0:29:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边挖个大洞,盛放垃圾或其他什么玩意.\N{\fs14}Dig a big hole over there to put the garbage in and what-have-you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.09,0:29:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把这些锅碗瓢盆都洗干净.\N{\fs14}Ik eep these pots and pans scrubbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.73,0:29:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不管干什么,不要把任何东西扔到Cove湾里.\N{\fs14}Don't put anything in the bay, whatever you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.54,0:29:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼,这就是你煮出来的汤吗?\N{\fs14}Holy smokes, cook! You call that soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.20,0:29:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不,长官,那是洗碗水.\N{\fs14}No, sir, that's dishwater.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.28,0:29:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,准尉...\N{\fs14}Ensigns.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.12,0:29:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们已经厌烦了...\N{\fs14}I suppose you're getting tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.12,0:29:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,来回送信及日常的巡逻.\N{\fs14}...of all this routine messenger and patrol duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们一定很想找机会 证明你们关于鱼雷快艇的理论.\N{\fs14}I know you're anxious to prove your theory of the motor torpedo boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.00,0:29:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也知道...\N{\fs14}As you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.01,0:30:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人夺取了苏比克湾.\N{\fs14}...the Japs have Subic Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.31,0:30:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在巴朗牙堡垒调了艘巡洋舰, 轰击我们在巴丹的阵地.\N{\fs14}They've got a cruiser at Fort Balanga shelling our positions on Bataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.88,0:30:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要么击沉它,\N{\fs14}We've either got to sink her...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就只能撤退.\N{\fs14}...or pull out our troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.45,0:30:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,科雷吉多尔, 西西曼湾,苏比克.\N{\fs14}Corregidor, Sisiman Cove, Subic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是战线.\N{\fs14}The lines are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.22,0:30:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人在这布设了水雷.\N{\fs14}The Jap minefields here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.19,0:30:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的巡洋舰...\N{\fs14}Their cruiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.83,0:30:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在这儿...\N{\fs14}...there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.67,0:30:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,去击沉它.\N{\fs14}Sink her.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.60,0:30:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起,长官.借我用用.\N{\fs14}Excuse me, sir, may I borrow that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.75,0:30:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一艘艇就行,你呢,莱恩?\N{\fs14}I think one boat, don't you, Mr. Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.25,0:30:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不,布里克雷,我想需要两艘.\N{\fs14}No, I think two boats, Mr. Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.59,0:30:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去两条艇,长官.\N{\fs14}Two boats, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.26,0:30:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,黄昏出发.\N{\fs14}Shove off at dusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.29,0:30:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安.\N{\fs14}Good evening, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.23,0:31:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没那么多钢盔,\N{\fs14}We haven't got enough steel helmets to go around...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.54,0:31:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只给你们枪炮手和鱼雷操作员配发钢盔.\N{\fs14}...so issue them to your gunners and torpedo men.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.72,0:31:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我再重复一遍..\N{\fs14}I repeat again...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.35,0:31:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要使用无线电,除非你肯定 确实已经被日本人发现了\N{\fs14}...do not open up on your radios until you're sure they've spotted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.62,0:31:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被发现,用12.7mm机枪打灭探照灯.\N{\fs14}Use your 50-calibers to knock out the searchlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.66,0:31:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说派两艘艇去,另一艘派谁去?\N{\fs14}You said there'd be two boats. Who's the second?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.20,0:31:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,34号艇,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Rusty with the 34 boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,我们18:00出发.\N{\fs14}That's all. We'll shove off about 1800.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.74,0:31:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我来算下航速..\N{\fs14}I'll regulate the speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.34,0:31:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在天黑时到达这里.\N{\fs14}...so we'll reach the end of this leg here in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.87,0:31:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,安迪.\N{\fs14}All right, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好,我们走,马汉.\N{\fs14}All right, let's go, Mahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.62,0:31:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-长官.. - 嗯?\N{\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.55,0:31:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么...\N{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.92,0:31:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-长官? -没门,索悌,\N{\fs14}- Sir? - Not a chance, Shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.16,0:32:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抄一份送给安迪,他在34号艇.\N{\fs14}Copy that in longhand and give it to Andy on the 34 boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.33,0:32:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,积极的家伙.\N{\fs14}Eager beavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.30,0:32:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事?我的艇是最好的艇.\N{\fs14}What's the matter with us? We have the best boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我的是最快的艇.\N{\fs14}And my boat's the fastest one in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.57,0:32:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,17:30\N{\fs14}Seventeen-thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.34,0:32:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,医生,你来看下我的手指...\N{\fs14}Doc, will you take a look at this finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.42,0:32:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子..\N{\fs14}Fellas...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.05,0:32:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最终获准..\N{\fs14}...we finally got the green light...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.69,0:32:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,去击沉苏比克湾里的一艘日本巡洋舰.\N{\fs14}...to sink a Jap cruiser in Subic Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.73,0:32:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要穿过这片日本人的水雷区和炮火覆盖区, 后面是他们的巡逻艇.\N{\fs14}Through those Jap mines, artillery and past them patrol boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.66,0:32:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们肯定有一艘能回来.\N{\fs14}One of our boats ought to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.93,0:32:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你们如果不准时就赶不上了.\N{\fs14}Any of you guys not on time don't get to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.57,0:32:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,莎士比亚.\N{\fs14}All right, Shakespeare.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.81,0:32:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,肘部血液毒,你应该去医院.\N{\fs14}You got blood poison to the elbow. You belong in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.52,0:33:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来就去医院.\N{\fs14}When I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.99,0:33:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果你还想要胳膊,就得现在去医院. - 涂点碘酒,包扎一下.\N{\fs14}- If you don't want to lose it, go now. - Put iodine on it and wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.89,0:33:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了,医生.替我保密.\N{\fs14}Look, Doc, do me a favor. Ik eep your mouth shut about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.50,0:33:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了在蛋糕上撒点盐.\N{\fs14}Don't forget to put a pinch of salt in that pancake batter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.80,0:33:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我床铺下面有果酱,拿给他们.\N{\fs14}You'll find jam under my bunk. Give them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都准备好了,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}All set, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.81,0:33:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的胳膊没事吧? - 没事.\N{\fs14}- Your arm all right? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.48,0:33:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,准备完毕.\N{\fs14}Everything's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.82,0:33:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,施拉格,放松一下吧.\N{\fs14}Okay, Slug, relax until time to shove off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.46,0:33:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,拉斯悌!\N{\fs14}Hey, Rusty!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.73,0:33:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你的胳膊.\N{\fs14}Let me see that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.04,0:33:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去医务室,伙计.\N{\fs14}You're going to sick bay, fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.14,0:33:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克,你不是怕我抢你的功吧?\N{\fs14}You aren't afraid of a little competition, are you, Brick?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.31,0:34:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,索悌,34号艇不去了, 改派31号艇,让他们做好准备.\N{\fs14}Shorty, the 31 boat'll go instead of the 34. Get her ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.45,0:34:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想失去一个优秀的副手.\N{\fs14}I won't lose a good exec because you're out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.99,0:34:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把船停好.\N{\fs14}Secure the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.43,0:34:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,莫加西!\N{\fs14}Mulcahey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我会教训你的.\N{\fs14}For two bits, I'd punch you right in the mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.11,0:34:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道原因. - 知道.\N{\fs14}- You know the score. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.61,0:34:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的鱼雷操作员待命.\N{\fs14}And have your torpedo man stand by in case those circuits fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.52,0:34:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,起锚.\N{\fs14}Wind them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.89,0:34:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快!\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.63,0:34:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走.\N{\fs14}Let's go, Good Luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.82,0:35:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,护士!护士!\N{\fs14}Corpsman! Corpsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.06,0:35:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嚷嚷什么?这是医院.\N{\fs14}This is a hospital. Why don't you hire a hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.40,0:35:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把帽子摘了.\N{\fs14}Take off your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.94,0:36:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只是手指被割伤了,我没有...\N{\fs14}It's just a little cut along the finger. I don't-
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.34,0:36:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,衬衫到那有点难脱.\N{\fs14}Shirts are hard to get out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.24,0:36:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,假臂也是.\N{\fs14}So are artificial arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,海军的.\N{\fs14}Anchors aweigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.17,0:37:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你发烧了,43度.\N{\fs14}You've got a temperature a little over 103.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.97,0:37:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了这些药片.\N{\fs14}Chew these sulfur pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.94,0:37:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是弹片? - 是的.\N{\fs14}What is this, shrapnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.15,0:37:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么受的伤?\N{\fs14}Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.51,0:37:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在甲米地湾.\N{\fs14}Cavite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.42,0:37:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没伤到.\N{\fs14}It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没受伤??\N{\fs14}It doesn't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.05,0:37:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你没听过血液毒吗?\N{\fs14}Did you ever hear of blood poisoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.49,0:37:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你再晚来几小时, 就必须截肢了.\N{\fs14}If you'd been a few hours later, I'd have had to take that arm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.83,0:37:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,指挥部通知说伤员2小时后到.\N{\fs14}Headquarters called. Casualties arriving in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.77,0:37:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-有多少伤员? -200多.\N{\fs14}- How many? - Over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.83,0:37:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那得快点.赶紧休息一下.\N{\fs14}Double deckers. Try and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.34,0:37:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有的忙了.那个年轻人病了.\N{\fs14}We've got work to do. That young man is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.01,0:37:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,给他降降温,想办法让他睡着.\N{\fs14}Get his temperature down and get him to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.74,0:37:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后休息一下.\N{\fs14}Take a few minutes yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.58,0:38:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你发烧了,最好躺下.\N{\fs14}You'd better lie down. You have a temperature of 103.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.45,0:38:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道.\N{\fs14}So I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.49,0:38:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们海军总是比正常人高两度.\N{\fs14}You Navy boys always run about two degrees above normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.36,0:38:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么军衔?\N{\fs14}Must be the time spent at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.59,0:38:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么军衔?\N{\fs14}What is your rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.63,0:38:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,陆军少尉.\N{\fs14}Second lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.96,0:38:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而我是海军中尉,所以请注意你的言语.\N{\fs14}I'm a j. g., so watch your language.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.50,0:38:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喔,我还以为你是骑警呢.\N{\fs14}I thought you were a motorcycle cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.97,0:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你官阶高,不过这轮不上你发话.\N{\fs14}Despite your gold braid, you don't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.64,0:38:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,乖乖躺下吧.\N{\fs14}We tell you. So lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.78,0:38:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,脱裤子.\N{\fs14}Unfasten your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.72,0:38:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-你说什么? -我说,脱裤子.\N{\fs14}- What? - Unfasten your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.99,0:38:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-脱裤子.\N{\fs14}Unfasten your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.48,0:39:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,往右一点.\N{\fs14}Come right a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.42,0:39:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,靠右.\N{\fs14}Right a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.59,0:39:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,现在应该到雷区了.\N{\fs14}This should be the minefields now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.39,0:39:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,往左一点.\N{\fs14}Left a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.53,0:39:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,靠左.\N{\fs14}Left easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.20,0:39:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,稳住.\N{\fs14}Steady as she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.27,0:39:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-隆格 的艇上有信号吗? -长官,看不见他.\N{\fs14}- Any sign of Long's boat? - Don't see him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.53,0:39:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-出什么毛病了? -汽油里面有石蜡.\N{\fs14}- What's wrong? - This gas was loaded with wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.30,0:39:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,发动机罢工了.\N{\fs14}Sabotage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.36,0:39:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-要多久能修好? -大约要40分钟.\N{\fs14}- How long to get started? - About 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.87,0:39:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量快点.\N{\fs14}Hurry it all you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.94,0:40:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得花40分钟修理.\N{\fs14}Forty-minute job.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.27,0:40:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想俘虏我们.\N{\fs14}They're trying to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.74,0:40:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,打掉那盏灯!\N{\fs14}Get that light!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.76,0:40:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,弃船!\N{\fs14}Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.53,0:40:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,弃船!\N{\fs14}Abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.79,0:40:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,31号艇被击中了,长官.\N{\fs14}The shore batteries got the 31 boat, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.92,0:40:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷准备.\N{\fs14}Stand by your torpedo tubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.47,0:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,预--备\N{\fs14}Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.18,0:41:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire one!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.31,0:41:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,二号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire two!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.24,0:44:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-唔,厨子,我们成功了. -什么成功了?\N{\fs14}- Well, Cookie, we did it. - Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.01,0:44:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪了?\N{\fs14}Been someplace?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.11,0:44:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把小日本的巡洋舰炸沉了.\N{\fs14}We blew that Jap cruiser into next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.62,0:44:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,是吗?\N{\fs14}Recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.95,0:44:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吃东西了吗?\N{\fs14}Pick up any chow?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.12,0:44:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,米克,我忘了告诉你了, 你的衣服泡胀了,.\N{\fs14}I forgot to tell you, Mick, your laundry's drying. Came out swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还错过了一顿丰盛的早餐.\N{\fs14}You guys were late for breakfast too. It was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对,葡萄的水果蛋糕.\N{\fs14}Yeah, cupcakes with raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.09,0:44:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听着,你这大嘴巴.\N{\fs14}Listen, bigmouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.63,0:44:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是个大家伙,配有232mm大炮...\N{\fs14}That ship was a big, converted job with eight-inch guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.40,0:44:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们把它炸上了天.\N{\fs14}...and we blew her into kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.82,0:44:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是汤普金斯.\N{\fs14}Tompkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.02,0:44:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么会这样? -他是机枪手.\N{\fs14}- How? - Machine gun in the belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.35,0:44:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还失去了31号艇.\N{\fs14}Yes, and we lost the 31 boat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.94,0:45:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们部队昨晚在巴丹给日本人来了一击.\N{\fs14}Our club on Bataan took another rap on the chin last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.35,0:45:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们海军去哪了?\N{\fs14}Where is that Navy of yours, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.52,0:45:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在纽约中央公园小湖里吗?\N{\fs14}On Central Park Lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.75,0:45:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那会很孤独的.\N{\fs14}They'll be along.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.42,0:45:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要到圣诞节才能再见到他们.\N{\fs14}We won't see them till Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.36,0:45:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想,那时候,我们的空军已经打赢了这场战争了.\N{\fs14}By then the Air Force will have won the war, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.83,0:45:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是空军在哪儿呢?\N{\fs14}Only, where is the Air Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.58,0:45:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,敌机来袭.\N{\fs14}Enemy aircraft approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.41,0:45:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭所有通风机和隔仓.\N{\fs14}Secure all ventilators and bulkheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.12,0:45:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一遍:敌机来袭.\N{\fs14}Repeat: Enemy aircraft approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.22,0:45:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,关闭所有..\N{\fs14}Secure all...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.12,0:45:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,通风机和隔仓.\N{\fs14}...ventilators and bulkheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.38,0:47:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,身边有那样女孩真好...\N{\fs14}That's a nice kind of a girl to have around...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.28,0:47:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在战争时期...\N{\fs14}...in wartime.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.95,0:47:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,任何时候.\N{\fs14}Or anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.02,0:47:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她...\N{\fs14}She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.09,0:47:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那样可爱.\N{\fs14}...kind of cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.29,0:47:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都这么认为的.\N{\fs14}11,000 guys can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.73,0:47:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧.呃?\N{\fs14}Pretty tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.60,0:47:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些小姑娘为什么不歇会?\N{\fs14}Why don't you girls get some rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.60,0:47:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我们不想吗?\N{\fs14}Don't think we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.17,0:47:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑一下?\N{\fs14}How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.24,0:47:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去问问那个又高又黑的讨厌鬼吗?\N{\fs14}Going to ask tall, dark and obnoxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.15,0:47:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上要跳舞呢,去弄漂亮一点.\N{\fs14}Got to look pretty for that dance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.85,0:48:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,胳膊怎样了?\N{\fs14}How's the arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.45,0:48:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没事.\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.92,0:48:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗.去跳舞吗?\N{\fs14}Good. Would you like to go to a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.49,0:48:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不,我不跳舞的.\N{\fs14}Listen, sister, I don't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.26,0:48:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也不想去学跳舞.\N{\fs14}And I can't take time out now to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.03,0:48:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想离开这儿.\N{\fs14}All I want to do is get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.61,0:48:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你等一等.\N{\fs14}Now, wait a minute before you start popping off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.91,0:48:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不在乎她们怎么样.\N{\fs14}I don't care if they dance their dogs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.55,0:48:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讲点道理吧.她们也需要放松一下.\N{\fs14}Be reasonable. Those girls need relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.19,0:48:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,需要做点什么提醒她们..\N{\fs14}Something to remind them they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.35,0:48:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她们是女人.\N{\fs14}...women!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.39,0:48:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没错.\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.52,0:48:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可没人提醒我我是什么.\N{\fs14}They're not going to remind me of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.16,0:48:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是一个...\N{\fs14}All uglied up in those...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.06,0:48:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,丑陋的乡巴佬..\N{\fs14}...potato bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.80,0:50:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好. -你好.\N{\fs14}- Hello. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.01,0:50:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的舞会.\N{\fs14}Nice party.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.94,0:50:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,既然来了,不妨多呆一会吧.\N{\fs14}Now that you're here, why don't you stay a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.21,0:50:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,不了.我来这是为了..\N{\fs14}Oh, no, I just came over to...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.58,0:50:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你...\N{\fs14}...thank you for...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.08,0:50:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,呃,谢谢你帮我补好了衬衫.\N{\fs14}...you know, sewing up my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.78,0:50:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但你根本就会跳舞,对吗?\N{\fs14}But you do dance, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.83,0:50:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好,莱恩先生.\N{\fs14}Good evening, Mr. Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.24,0:50:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.\N{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.48,0:51:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得把胳膊放回吊床上更好吗?\N{\fs14}Think you better put that arm back in the sling?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.01,0:51:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定什么时候你要用它.\N{\fs14}You might use it someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.45,0:51:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,犁地,剪裁纸娃娃.\N{\fs14}...for plowing, or cutting out paper dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.52,0:51:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么在意?\N{\fs14}Why the eager interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.85,0:51:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,职业习惯?\N{\fs14}Professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.40,0:51:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉象回到家一样,对吗?\N{\fs14}It's rather like back home, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.27,0:51:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,门廊,\N{\fs14}The porch...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.91,0:51:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,吊床,\N{\fs14}...hammock...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.11,0:51:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,萤火虫..\N{\fs14}...fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.51,0:51:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你家在哪?\N{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.05,0:51:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,衣阿华州.\N{\fs14}Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.91,0:51:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道,高大的玉米林.\N{\fs14}You know, tall corn.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.52,0:51:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢?\N{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.59,0:51:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,上纽约州.\N{\fs14}Upper New York State.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.59,0:51:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs14}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.89,0:52:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果.\N{\fs14}...apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.71,0:52:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那些炮的火光\N{\fs14}Those gun flashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.01,0:52:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来就象萤火虫一般.\N{\fs14}...look like fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.92,0:52:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,每个夜晚,\N{\fs14}Every night...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.38,0:52:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,它们越来越近.\N{\fs14}...they come a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.29,0:53:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Hi, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.66,0:53:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,桑蒂,这是布里克雷上尉.\N{\fs14}Sandy, this is Lt. Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.66,0:53:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 迪邬斯小姐. - 你好.\N{\fs14}- Miss Davyss. - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.06,0:53:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-你好.\N{\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.10,0:53:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,舞会不错吧?\N{\fs14}Nice party?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.07,0:53:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒.\N{\fs14}Swell!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.07,0:53:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,舞跳得怎样呢?-\N{\fs14}That big lug dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.44,0:53:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了.\N{\fs14}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.31,0:53:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只踩到她一次.\N{\fs14}Only stepped on her foot once.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.24,0:53:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事?\N{\fs14}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.21,0:53:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等会再说好了.\N{\fs14}It can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.82,0:53:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你们谈好了.\N{\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.74,0:54:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪很利索就把巡洋舰干掉了.\N{\fs14}Andy did a pretty good job on the cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.25,0:54:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的只有加德纳...\N{\fs14}All we've got left is Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.25,0:54:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哦,他还太那么年轻..\N{\fs14}He's such a young kid for-
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.38,0:54:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这任务要求心灵手巧.\N{\fs14}It's tricky duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.96,0:54:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢?\N{\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.73,0:54:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.23,0:54:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他的手有多糟?\N{\fs14}Just how bad is that hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.97,0:54:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,手指一直裂到骨头,感染还没好.-\N{\fs14}The finger is open to the bone. And there's still infection there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.24,0:54:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找医生谈谈去.\N{\fs14}Let's go talk to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.11,0:54:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的指头是不是正在好转?\N{\fs14}Is it healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.38,0:54:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的.\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.58,0:54:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快点,布里克,帮我把帽子戴上.\N{\fs14}Come on, Brick. Help me pour the heat on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.92,0:55:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样？\N{\fs14}How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.02,0:55:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有人阵亡吗?\N{\fs14}Did you lose anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.09,0:55:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有,长官.\N{\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.72,0:55:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩先生把我们都救上来了.\N{\fs14}Mr. Ryan picked us up beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.92,0:55:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起,长官.\N{\fs14}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.33,0:55:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁愿失去的是自己的胳膊而不是33号艇.\N{\fs14}I'd rather lose my right arm than the 33 boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.60,0:56:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别那样想.\N{\fs14}Couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.00,0:56:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会成功的.\N{\fs14}Paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.47,0:56:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是,长官.\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.20,0:56:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.-\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.41,0:56:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪被7.7mm枪弹打穿了脚踝.\N{\fs14}Andy got a 7.7 through both ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.71,0:56:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哎,斯奈克.\N{\fs14}Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.42,0:56:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你接替安迪指挥34号艇.\N{\fs14}Take Andy's place on the 34 boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.05,0:56:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是,长官.\N{\fs14}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.83,0:56:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,运气有点背啊,安迪.\N{\fs14}That's tough luck, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.94,0:56:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,伤口好点吗?\N{\fs14}How're they feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.57,0:56:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不好.\N{\fs14}They don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.54,0:56:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,需要什么尽管说.\N{\fs14}You give us the word if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.44,0:56:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管说.\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.01,0:56:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会去看你的.\N{\fs14}We'll be over to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.65,0:56:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等你好了再回来指挥.\N{\fs14}The job's yours again when you can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.95,0:56:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我下周...\N{\fs14}I'll give you the nudge...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.89,0:56:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就回来.\N{\fs14}...about next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.49,0:57:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,收缆.\N{\fs14}Wind them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你从未见过那场面. 我们把小日本炸沉了!\N{\fs14}You never saw nothing like it. We blew that Nip out of the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.92,0:57:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-两条鱼雷,正中要害. -是这样的,米克.\N{\fs14}- Two fish, right in the guts. - Get this, Mick.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.35,0:57:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始是这样...\N{\fs14}We started to run like this-
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.09,0:57:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,早餐是杯形蛋糕.\N{\fs14}We had cupcakes for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.06,0:57:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,加葡萄干.\N{\fs14}With raisins.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.89,0:58:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 欢迎来做客,迪邬斯小姐. -谢谢.晚上好.\N{\fs14}- Glad to see you aboard, Miss Davyss. - Thank you. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.32,0:58:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们,我来介绍...\N{\fs14}Gentlemen, I would like to present...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.89,0:58:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩先生的客人,迪邬斯小姐.\N{\fs14}...Mr. Ryan's guest, Miss Davyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.36,0:58:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是--\N{\fs14}This is a-
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.96,0:58:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等一下.\N{\fs14}Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.73,0:58:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,隆格先生.\N{\fs14}Mr. Long.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.13,0:58:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸会. -幸会.\N{\fs14}- It's a pleasure to have you here. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.60,0:58:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-艾肯先生. -你好.\N{\fs14}- Mr. Aiken. - How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.24,0:58:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好.\N{\fs14}How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.74,0:58:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,加德纳先生.\N{\fs14}Mr. Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.51,0:58:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-幸会. -幸会.\N{\fs14}- Nice having you here. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.28,0:59:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-科斯先生. - 很高兴认识你. -你好.\N{\fs14}- And Mr. Cross. - Very happy to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.26,0:59:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请用晚餐,先生.\N{\fs14}Dinner is served, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.66,0:59:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.93,0:59:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐这个位置.\N{\fs14}Will you take my place at the head of the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.61,0:59:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌在科雷吉多尔岛上的医院里时, 是迪邬斯小姐在照料他.\N{\fs14}Miss Davyss took care of Rusty when he was in the hospital at Corregidor.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.05,0:59:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她隶属于巴丹半岛的野战医院.\N{\fs14}She's now attached to the field hospital at Bataan peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.02,0:59:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在巴丹半岛这还有护士?\N{\fs14}There are nurses over here on Bataan?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.36,0:59:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些吧.\N{\fs14}A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.23,0:59:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么其他的姑娘没来,...\N{\fs14}Wasn't it mean enough for you in Corregidor...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.53,0:59:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你在科雷吉多尔呆厌了?\N{\fs14}...without sending you girls over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.10,0:59:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,是我要求的.\N{\fs14}Well, I asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.37,1:00:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,在这,我偶尔可以和拉斯悌通电话.\N{\fs14}Over here, I can talk to Rusty sometimes on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.81,1:00:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏乔治,我们现在是邻居了.\N{\fs14}By George, we're neighbors now!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.64,1:00:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把其他姑娘也带来,我们举行个舞会.\N{\fs14}Next time, bring the other girls. We'll have a dance!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.78,1:00:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意!\N{\fs14}Be a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.85,1:00:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真开心.\N{\fs14}This is a lovely party.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.85,1:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,非常棒.\N{\fs14}It's swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.86,1:00:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.46,1:00:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-班尼. -是,长官.\N{\fs14}- Benny. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.90,1:00:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.37,1:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,汤.\N{\fs14}Soup.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.45,1:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,热的.\N{\fs14}Hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.82,1:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,烤饼,味道很好的.\N{\fs14}Biscuits, very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.89,1:00:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.59,1:00:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的果酱,长官.-\N{\fs14}Real jam, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.83,1:01:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,汤,烤饼,果酱.\N{\fs14}Soup, biscuits, jam.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.33,1:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是要说一遍,一流的晚会.\N{\fs14}I still say it's a swell party.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.50,1:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就差乐队和夜总会表演了.\N{\fs14}Now all we need is an orchestra and a floor show.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.10,1:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,迪邬斯,你将迎来人生最大的惊喜.\N{\fs14}Miss Davyss, you're in for the biggest surprise of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.14,1:01:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的女士\N{\fs14}Dear old girl
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.65,1:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知更鸟在..\N{\fs14}The robin...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.45,1:01:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在你头顶歌唱,\N{\fs14}...sings above you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.09,1:01:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的女士,\N{\fs14}Dear old girl
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.76,1:01:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它唱出的是我的爱意,\N{\fs14}It speaks of how I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.61,1:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我思念着失去的爱人\N{\fs14}The blinding tears are falling
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.79,1:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,泪流满面,\N{\fs14}As I think of my lost pearl
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.73,1:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我破碎的心在呼唤\N{\fs14}And my broken heart is calling
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.98,1:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,呼唤着你的名字\N{\fs14}Calling for you
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.48,1:02:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的女士\N{\fs14}Dear old girl
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.26,1:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪,太美妙了.\N{\fs14}Terrific! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.94,1:02:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呃,能允许我说几句吗?\N{\fs14}If you'll excuse me, I have a lot of checking to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.64,1:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,请.\N{\fs14}Surely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.05,1:03:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你能过来.\N{\fs14}Thank you very much for coming over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.59,1:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我们很有意义.\N{\fs14}It meant a great deal to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.02,1:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安,桑蒂.\N{\fs14}Good night, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.16,1:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安.\N{\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.56,1:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-我也走了.能叫你桑蒂吗? -当然可以.\N{\fs14}- Me too. Could I call you Sandy? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.83,1:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-好的,晚安. -晚安.\N{\fs14}- Well, good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.50,1:03:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.77,1:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安,桑蒂. -晚安.\N{\fs14}- Good night, Sandy. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.34,1:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没这么开心过,\N{\fs14}I don't know when I've had such a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.91,1:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了,我们现在是邻居了.\N{\fs14}And don't forget now, we're neighbors and everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.18,1:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安,拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Good night, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.67,1:03:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,晚餐怎么样?\N{\fs14}How's the chow?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.90,1:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了.\N{\fs14}Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.17,1:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,唉,孩子,如果能带你去亚利桑那号,\N{\fs14}Boy, if I had you on the old Arizona...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.77,1:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以做一个烤盘,把你头发弄卷.\N{\fs14}...I'd make a pot roast that'd make your hair curl.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.22,1:04:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你哭了?\N{\fs14}Crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.86,1:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没哭.\N{\fs14}I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.80,1:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只是他们这些人多好啊.\N{\fs14}It's just that they're such nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.27,1:04:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是开玩笑吧.\N{\fs14}You aren't kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.81,1:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷先生和莱恩先生到了.\N{\fs14}Mr. Brickley and Mr. Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.20,1:05:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是机密.\N{\fs14}Confidentially...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.60,1:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,总统命令我,\N{\fs14}...the President has ordered me...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.33,1:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,以及部分重要人员转移到澳大利亚.\N{\fs14}...and certain key personnel to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.07,1:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们用快艇送我们去棉兰老岛.\N{\fs14}Your boats will take us to Mindanao.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.81,1:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到那后,陆军航空队的轰炸机会送我们去南边.\N{\fs14}From there, an Army bomber will fly us south.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.91,1:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我们把全部4艘艇都派出去吗?\N{\fs14}You want to use all four of the boats?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.28,1:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,全派出去,让他们准备好.\N{\fs14}Yes. Get them ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.62,1:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是机密.\N{\fs14}This is secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.98,1:05:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重复一下,\N{\fs14}Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.12,1:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是机密.\N{\fs14}Secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.09,1:05:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出发日期决定后会通知你们.\N{\fs14}You'll get the date when it's set.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.89,1:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是,长官.\N{\fs14}Aye, aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.42,1:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一会.\N{\fs14}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.63,1:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们会需要这些海图的.\N{\fs14}I think you'll find all the charts you'll need.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.07,1:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们肯定也知道, 我们现在的处境不会好转.\N{\fs14}You know it's not going well with us up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.81,1:06:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听到消息了,长官.\N{\fs14}We get the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.68,1:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把兵力集中起来,组建一个海军营.\N{\fs14}We're scraping up all we can to form a naval battalion.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.38,1:06:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你能出几个人吗?\N{\fs14}Can you spare any men?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.75,1:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以出2个人,长官.\N{\fs14}We have two extra crews, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.65,1:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我用的着他们的,布里克雷.\N{\fs14}I could use them, Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.32,1:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明白,长官.\N{\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.13,1:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向南走600英里.\N{\fs14}We're going to run south 600 miles.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.06,1:06:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那天气很恶劣.\N{\fs14}There's bad weather out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.73,1:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,路上会很艰苦.\N{\fs14}It'll be rough going.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.50,1:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有船发生故障, 我们也只能扔下他们不管.\N{\fs14}If any boat breaks down, we'll have to let her go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.54,1:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道,只能牺牲他们了.\N{\fs14}Expendable. You know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.44,1:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,头天晚上去...\N{\fs14}First night's run...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.54,1:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,库约岛.\N{\fs14}...Cuyo Islands.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.71,1:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,白天我们要藏起来.\N{\fs14}Hole up there during the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.55,1:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天晚上去...\N{\fs14}Second night's run...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.02,1:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,棉兰老岛的卡加延.\N{\fs14}...to Cagayan on Mindanao.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.42,1:06:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那的机场还在我们手里, 但日本人推进很快.\N{\fs14}We still hold the airfield there, but the Japs are moving fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.86,1:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道机场还能守多久.\N{\fs14}It's a question of how long we can hang onto it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.49,1:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近陆地时要保持百倍警惕.\N{\fs14}Approach every landfall with caution.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.90,1:07:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,时刻做好战斗或撤退准备.\N{\fs14}Be prepared to fight or run for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.03,1:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但要记住,你们的首要任务是把这些人送出去.\N{\fs14}But remember, your primary duty is to get these people out.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.24,1:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌带将军上34号艇.\N{\fs14}Rusty will take the admiral on the 34 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.41,1:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢,带..\N{\fs14}And I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.08,1:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,陆军的人.\N{\fs14}...the Army personnel with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.18,1:07:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上21:00出发.\N{\fs14}We'll shove off at 2100.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.08,1:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,汽艇准备好了吗?\N{\fs14}Motor whaleboat ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.69,1:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,随时可以出发,长官.\N{\fs14}Whenever you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.79,1:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,莫加西能代我指挥一下吗?\N{\fs14}Could Mulcahey take over my duty?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.69,1:07:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去看看安迪.\N{\fs14}I'd like to go along and see Andy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.49,1:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呃,好吧.我们21:00出发.\N{\fs14}Yeah, sure. We'll shove off at 2100.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.70,1:07:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,轻点,把板子抬起来.\N{\fs14}Easy does it. Bring those boards up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.04,1:07:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这些油桶将在到达第一任务点时丢弃.\N{\fs14}These drums will go overboard on the first sea we hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.95,1:07:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,交叉绑牢.\N{\fs14}Cross lash them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.98,1:08:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,把它们放好放稳.\N{\fs14}Put them on right and tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.48,1:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才正跟他们这么说呢.\N{\fs14}That's exactly what I've been telling them.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.02,1:08:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,现在按船长和我说的去做.\N{\fs14}Let's do it how the captain and I want it done.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.64,1:08:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,我们把能带的都带上了.\N{\fs14}We can take all we got, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.38,1:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安德鲁斯先生怎么样了?\N{\fs14}How's Mr. Andrews?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.88,1:08:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说他过八九天就康复.\N{\fs14}Doctor says he's good for about eight or nine days.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.48,1:08:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你代我向他告别.\N{\fs14}Will you give him an aloha for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.60,1:09:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就2分钟\N{\fs14}Just for two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.97,1:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量装得高兴点吧\N{\fs14}Be cheerful and, you know, give him the old one-two-three.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.01,1:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好的.\N{\fs14}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.32,1:09:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,海,布里克.\N{\fs14}Hi, Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.86,1:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊...\N{\fs14}Hello...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.29,1:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,..伙计.\N{\fs14}...fellas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.76,1:09:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨,安迪. -嗨,伙计.\N{\fs14}- Hi, Andy. - Hi, fella.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.99,1:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怎样?\N{\fs14}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.06,1:09:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是咋了?\N{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.70,1:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷艇聚会吗?\N{\fs14}A PT boat convention?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.30,1:10:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真高兴.\N{\fs14}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.54,1:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来不错,安迪.\N{\fs14}You look swell, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.07,1:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算什么时候归队?\N{\fs14}When will you quit stalling and get back to work?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.04,1:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很快.\N{\fs14}Any day now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.81,1:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这饭店伙食如何啊?\N{\fs14}How's the chow in this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.71,1:10:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了.\N{\fs14}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.08,1:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,鸽肉,\N{\fs14}Squab.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.28,1:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,猪排.\N{\fs14}Steak.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.72,1:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-莫加西和马汉问你好. -还有厨子师.\N{\fs14}- Mulcahey and Mahan say hello. - Cookie too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.25,1:10:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的人.\N{\fs14}The whole gang.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.82,1:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-34号艇怎样? -很好.\N{\fs14}- How's the 34 boat? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.12,1:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想...\N{\fs14}I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.66,1:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,斯奈克正手忙脚乱的接手我的工作呢.\N{\fs14}...Snake's been botching up my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.79,1:10:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是安德鲁斯.\N{\fs14}He's no Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.56,1:10:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,我这有些香烟.\N{\fs14}Say, I got some cigarettes here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.23,1:10:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来,抽几根.\N{\fs14}Go on, have some.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.27,1:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不了.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.90,1:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正把他带上正轨,\N{\fs14}We're keeping him in condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.97,1:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-他正努力夺你的位置. -努力就对了.\N{\fs14}- He's trying to take your place. - Trying to is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.31,1:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备好了一次任务.\N{\fs14}We got a patrol to get ready for.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.61,1:10:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你复员,就有你的份.\N{\fs14}The job's yours anytime you can make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.45,1:10:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢. -下周再见.\N{\fs14}- Thanks. - See you next week.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.12,1:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见. -别急.\N{\fs14}- So long. - Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.46,1:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,头,我有话要说.\N{\fs14}Say, Skipper-
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.09,1:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐下,布里克.\N{\fs14}Sit down, Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.33,1:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们接受的任务很棒.\N{\fs14}That was a nice act you boys put on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.84,1:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你从那知道的.\N{\fs14}How did you get the word?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.41,1:11:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小道消息.\N{\fs14}Scuttlebutt.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.55,1:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-嘿,布里克. -呃,我来拿.\N{\fs14}Here. I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.79,1:11:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能活着,\N{\fs14}If you get through...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.09,1:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把这些寄出去,行吗?\N{\fs14}...mail these, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.36,1:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,我答应你.\N{\fs14}Sure, if there's any mail.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.76,1:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这封给我妈的.\N{\fs14}One to Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.83,1:11:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这封给迈拉.\N{\fs14}One to Myra.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.90,1:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的,她在洛克西德.\N{\fs14}You know, she's at Lockheed.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.11,1:11:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我还写好了遗嘱.\N{\fs14}I wrote out a will too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.58,1:11:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是都给自己安排好了.\N{\fs14}That was a pretty good act you put on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.12,1:11:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有什么没做好的事情...\N{\fs14}Any unfinished business that you want me...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.02,1:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮你完成吗?\N{\fs14}...to take care of for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.92,1:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,或要我向你家人转达什么特别的话...\N{\fs14}Anything particular you'd like to have me say to your folks...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.63,1:12:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或带给迈拉?\N{\fs14}...or to Myra?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.83,1:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我都写在信里了.\N{\fs14}I guess I've written about all I had to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.67,1:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉,我不能为中队做更多事情.\N{\fs14}Sorry I couldn't do more for the squadron.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.92,1:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗?\N{\fs14}Is there anybody on duty there?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.29,1:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接野战医院.\N{\fs14}Give me the field hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.09,1:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是海军中尉莱恩.\N{\fs14}This is Lt. Ryan speaking, Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.23,1:13:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫护士迪邬斯少尉接电话.\N{\fs14}I want to talk to one of your nurses. Lieutenant Davyss.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.70,1:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,桑蒂·迪邬斯.\N{\fs14}Sandy Davyss.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.73,1:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道她名字.\N{\fs14}I don't know her first name.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.40,1:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,只知道她叫桑蒂·迪邬斯.\N{\fs14}Sandy. Sandy Davyss.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.52,1:14:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,－喂,.. －呸,再喂也没用,.\N{\fs14}Oh, what's the use?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.82,1:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨,别着急.\N{\fs14}Here! Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.89,1:14:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有的是时间.\N{\fs14}You've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.10,1:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再试试嘛.\N{\fs14}Ik eep trying.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.40,1:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-把信号板拿来. -是,长官.\N{\fs14}- Bring that sign. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.65,1:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-立--正! -稍--息.\N{\fs14}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.99,1:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们大家都是好样的.\N{\fs14}You're a swell bunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.16,1:15:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸曾与你们共事.\N{\fs14}I'm glad to have been able to serve with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.53,1:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我本可以告诉你们...\N{\fs14}I'd like to be able to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.57,1:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说我们这次出动是去求援的.\N{\fs14}...that we were going out to bring back help.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.34,1:15:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但那不是实情.\N{\fs14}But that wouldn't be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.14,1:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要放弃这的防线去执行特别任务.\N{\fs14}We're going down the line to do a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.81,1:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而你们则要到巴丹去,加入陆军作战.\N{\fs14}You're going to Bataan with the Army.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.88,1:15:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们本来是海军,\N{\fs14}That isn't what you've been trained for.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.99,1:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在陆军需要你们.\N{\fs14}But they need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.86,1:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些...\N{\fs14}You older men...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.52,1:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老兵...\N{\fs14}...with longer service records...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.99,1:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要照顾好新兵.\N{\fs14}...take care of the kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.10,1:15:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,或许...\N{\fs14}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.87,1:15:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就说这么多吧.\N{\fs14}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.91,1:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,愿上帝保佑你们.\N{\fs14}God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.51,1:16:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-我是莱恩. -你好,拉斯悌. -你好,桑蒂.\N{\fs14}- Ryan speaking. - Hello, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.82,1:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,15号来找你方便吗?\N{\fs14}Is the 15th all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.72,1:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行,桑蒂.\N{\fs14}No, it isn't, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.49,1:16:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那16号行吗?\N{\fs14}Would the 16th be better?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.83,1:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哪天都不行.\N{\fs14}Nothing would be better.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.73,1:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,到底怎么了?\N{\fs14}Well, what is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.80,1:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们该说再见了.\N{\fs14}I guess it's goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.91,1:16:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我你要去哪吗?\N{\fs14}Can you tell me where you're going?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.91,1:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行.\N{\fs14}I wish I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.32,1:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你还回来吗?\N{\fs14}Are you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.19,1:17:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道.\N{\fs14}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.92,1:17:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想是不会回来了.\N{\fs14}But I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.43,1:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...那么,这次是真的再见了?\N{\fs14}Well, this is really goodbye, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.63,1:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经一切都那么美好,对吗?\N{\fs14}It's been awfully nice, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.04,1:17:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经那么美好.\N{\fs14}It's been swell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.67,1:17:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,桑蒂,你知道,我不会说话.\N{\fs14}Look, Sandy, I'm no good at talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.28,1:17:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给你写了封信,你很快就会收到.\N{\fs14}I've written you a letter. Shorty Long will get it to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.85,1:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起小姐,我们得把它带走了. 我们要向南方转移.\N{\fs14}Sorry, miss. We got to take this out. We're moving south.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.35,1:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,总机?\N{\fs14}Operator?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.69,1:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么把我们挂断了?\N{\fs14}You've cut us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.86,1:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有将军要线路?不能等我们讲完吗?\N{\fs14}A couple of generals? Couldn't they wait till we were through?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.44,1:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,汽艇来了,长官.\N{\fs14}Motor whaleboat coming alongside, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.11,1:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再接迪邬斯小姐.\N{\fs14}Put Miss Davyss back on the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.82,1:18:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,总机,线路怎么了?\N{\fs14}Operator, what's gone wrong with this line?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.12,1:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,断了.\N{\fs14}Gone dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.29,1:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很麻烦,长官.\N{\fs14}That's tough, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.79,1:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,希望那什么将军确实在说重要的事.\N{\fs14}Hope what those generals had to say was important.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.96,1:18:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-再见,医生. -再见,长官.\N{\fs14}- So long, Doc. - Goodbye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.93,1:18:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,威尔.\N{\fs14}So long, Willie.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.43,1:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-好好干. -是,长官.\N{\fs14}- Be a good kid. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.94,1:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-再见,斯利姆. -再见.\N{\fs14}- So long, Slim. - So long.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.77,1:18:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你平安,萨米. -也祝你平安,宝贝.\N{\fs14}- Shalom aleichem, Sammy. - Same to you, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.84,1:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-再见,菲尔. -你们现在是陆军了.\N{\fs14}- So long, Phil, old boy. - You're in the Army now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.79,1:18:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-准备好了,布里克雷. -长官,准备就绪.\N{\fs14}- Ready, Brickley. - Ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.57,1:20:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,请在我帽子上签个名.\N{\fs14}Sir, please autograph my hat.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.04,1:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯,当然可以.\N{\fs14}Why, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.14,1:20:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚上好,长官.\N{\fs14}Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.25,1:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,莱恩.\N{\fs14}Ready, Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.42,1:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,收缆.\N{\fs14}Wind them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.54,1:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧,晦气. 快走!\N{\fs14}Come on, Bad Luck. Scat!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.37,1:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,列队!\N{\fs14}Fall in!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.14,1:21:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,向右转!\N{\fs14}Right face!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.81,1:21:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,原地踏步!\N{\fs14}Ground step!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.11,1:21:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,齐--步...\N{\fs14}Forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.38,1:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,走!\N{\fs14}March!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.83,1:23:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很准时.\N{\fs14}On time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.80,1:23:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只来了3艘.\N{\fs14}Only three boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.57,1:23:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是损失了一艘\N{\fs14}Must have lost one.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.25,1:25:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么命令,长官.\N{\fs14}Orders, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.32,1:25:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-中队留下来归马丁将军指挥. -是,长官.\N{\fs14}The squadron will work down here under General Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.39,1:25:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在巴丹还有几个人, 我打算去把他们接来.\N{\fs14}We've got quite a few men at Bataan. I'd like to go pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.57,1:25:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-你在那已经尽力了. -明白了,长官.\N{\fs14}You've done all you can up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.94,1:25:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,航空汽油呢?-\N{\fs14}What about aviation gasoline?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.35,1:25:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会设法弄来的.\N{\fs14}We'll try to find what you need.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.38,1:25:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那鱼雷呢?\N{\fs14}What about torpedoes?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.75,1:25:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在Cebu可能还有点,我去查一下.\N{\fs14}There may be some at Cebu. I'll inquire.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.92,1:25:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定得弄到航空汽油和鱼雷才行.\N{\fs14}We've got to have aviation gas and torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.56,1:25:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白.\N{\fs14}I realize that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.26,1:25:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把敌军的动静通知你们的.\N{\fs14}We'll keep you informed as to enemy activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.63,1:25:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,关于打击日本舰队的这个问题, 你们可以自行出击.\N{\fs14}Plan your own operations against their ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.53,1:26:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但每天都要向我报告你们的活动.\N{\fs14}But report to me daily by phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.61,1:26:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-再见,布里克雷. -再见,长官.\N{\fs14}- Goodbye, Brickley. - Goodbye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.84,1:26:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩.\N{\fs14}Ryan.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.98,1:26:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,长官.\N{\fs14}Goodbye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.46,1:26:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是倒霉透顶,怎么弄的?\N{\fs14}That's tough luck. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.29,1:26:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,机油失效,所有轴承都烧毁了.\N{\fs14}Oil failure. Burnt out every cock-eyed bearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.66,1:26:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,宿务那有船坞,我们拖你们去.\N{\fs14}There's a shipyard at Cebu. We'll tow you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.00,1:26:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-最好把发动机拆了. -我已经在拆了.\N{\fs14}- Better tear down those engines. - I've already started.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.34,1:26:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们拖我们去那.\N{\fs14}Thanks for the tow.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.74,1:26:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢.\N{\fs14}Por nada.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.71,1:26:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会报答你的.\N{\fs14}Do the same for you someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.48,1:26:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不希望那种事落到我头上.\N{\fs14}I hope not.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.08,1:26:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想想那些32号艇的家伙.\N{\fs14}Wonder about the kids on the 32 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.65,1:26:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-早上3点那会还在我们正横位置.\N{\fs14}They were abeam of us at 3:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.32,1:26:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就不见了.\N{\fs14}Then we missed them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.16,1:26:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-不会是被巡洋舰击中了吧?\N{\fs14}Suppose that cruiser got them?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.03,1:27:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别操心了,布里克.\N{\fs14}Stop worrying, Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.59,1:27:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会出现的.\N{\fs14}They'll show up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.76,1:27:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去机场.\N{\fs14}I'm going over to the airfield.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.33,1:27:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,搭架联络机去找找他们.\N{\fs14}Pick up an old crate, see if I can find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.57,1:27:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你代我指挥,嗯?\N{\fs14}Take over, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.47,1:27:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-别着急. -检查一下支板.\N{\fs14}- Take it easy. - Have a look at that plank.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.67,1:27:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当心珊瑚.\N{\fs14}And watch out for the coral.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.14,1:27:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,能注意听一下吗,大家注意.\N{\fs14}Can I have your attention? Attention, all hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.71,1:27:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷先生要我宣读这个声明:\N{\fs14}Mr. Brickley has requested that I make the following announcement:
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.92,1:27:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,中队的全体军官及士兵...\N{\fs14}For every officer and man in this squadron...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.49,1:27:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,由于你们在当前这张战争中表现出的勇气\N{\fs14}...for your work in the war to date-
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.32,1:27:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈皮,去那帮他一把.\N{\fs14}Happy, get in there and give him a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.09,1:27:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,将军...\N{\fs14}The General...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.80,1:27:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,授予你们...\N{\fs14}...has awarded the Silver Star...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.93,1:27:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,银星奖章.\N{\fs14}...for gallantry.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.33,1:27:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,祖尼,过去帮他.\N{\fs14}Junior, get in and help him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.54,1:27:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,支板松了,底下全是珊瑚.\N{\fs14}Planking's loose. The bottom's full of coral.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.34,1:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这下可好了.\N{\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.22,1:28:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息.\N{\fs14}Got a little news.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.42,1:28:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,中队的全体军官和士兵..\N{\fs14}To every officer and man in this squadron...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.66,1:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,由于你们在战争中的表现...\N{\fs14}...for your work in the war to date-
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.39,1:28:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起,长官.\N{\fs14}Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.66,1:28:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这只黑猫这段时间一直呆在这艘艇上.\N{\fs14}All this time, this black cat has been aboard this boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.76,1:28:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,将军授予银星奖章以表彰你们展现出的勇气.\N{\fs14}The General has awarded the Silver Star for gallantry.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.00,1:28:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便说下,这只猫本该在32号艇的.\N{\fs14}By rights, the cat ought to have been aboard the 32 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.10,1:28:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是它给我们41号艇带来了好运.\N{\fs14}Maybe this black cat is good luck for us, the 41 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.24,1:28:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听到没,你们被授予银猫奖章.\N{\fs14}Anyway, you've been awarded the Silver Cat.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.16,1:28:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,找到他们了吗?\N{\fs14}Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.10,1:28:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没发现.\N{\fs14}Not a sign of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.02,1:29:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了.\N{\fs14}Fire in the paint locker.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.19,1:29:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,马汉,怎么会这样?\N{\fs14}All right, Mahan. Think fast. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.86,1:29:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我,长官.\N{\fs14}It's all my fault, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.97,1:29:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟莫加西说...\N{\fs14}You see, I says to Mulcahey...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.60,1:29:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们给大伙弄点啤酒来吧"\N{\fs14}..."Let's get the crews a couple of beers. "
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.94,1:29:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是我听到过的最蠢的理由.\N{\fs14}That's the dumbest excuse I ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.01,1:29:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-对不起.\N{\fs14}- I'm sorry. - That helps!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.71,1:29:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们醒过来,它就成这模样了.\N{\fs14}So when we gets back, she was high and dry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.94,1:29:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,发动机启动不了了.都是我的错.\N{\fs14}The engines wouldn't start. It's just as much my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.15,1:29:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴.我的事我自己来扛.\N{\fs14}Pipe down. I'll take the rap.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.95,1:29:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼去吧,我要把你们两个都降为二等兵.\N{\fs14}For two cents, I'd bust you both to seaman second.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.48,1:29:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你多嘴.\N{\fs14}Ik eep your mouth out of my business.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.12,1:29:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,舵轮,支柱和轴全都坏了,长官.\N{\fs14}Everything, sir. Wheels, struts and shafts.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.50,1:30:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-是我的错. -怎么发生的?\N{\fs14}- It's my fault. - How'd it happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.27,1:30:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-不能怪别人. -到底怎么发生的?\N{\fs14}- There's no one else to blame. - How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.27,1:30:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的.\N{\fs14}It's like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.41,1:30:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们又热又累又渴.\N{\fs14}We were hot, tired and thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.34,1:30:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我和施拉格就喝了点啤酒...\N{\fs14}Slug and I thought we'd get some beer-
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.55,1:30:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在41号艇待命,把它拖走检查损伤情况.\N{\fs14}Stand by with the 41 boat. We'll pull her off and see the damage.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.35,1:30:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-是,长官.但我不想... -啤酒怎么样?\N{\fs14}- Yes, sir, but I don't want- - How was the beer?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.75,1:30:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一点都没喝.\N{\fs14}We didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.95,1:30:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,35号艇已准备好.\N{\fs14}Ready on the 35 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.02,1:30:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,35号艇已准备好.\N{\fs14}Ready on the 35 boat!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.51,1:31:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,重复命令.\N{\fs14}Repeat the instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.92,1:31:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,如果受到攻击,就将艇烧毁, 我们会来搭救你们的.\N{\fs14}If you're attacked, burn your boats. We'll try and pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.15,1:31:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果受到攻击,\N{\fs14}If we're attacked...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.15,1:31:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将艇烧毁...\N{\fs14}...burn your boats.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.86,1:31:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来搭救你们.\N{\fs14}And we'll try to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.56,1:32:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,乔斯,费尔南德斯·玛丽亚!\N{\fs14}Jos?Fernandez Maria!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.09,1:32:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,到那边去.\N{\fs14}Get going there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.63,1:32:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都给我好好干活!\N{\fs14}I'll whop you with a neck yoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.13,1:32:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂,布里克!\N{\fs14}Brick!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.40,1:32:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,左舷支柱和轴弯了.\N{\fs14}Got a bent strut and shaft on the port side.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.90,1:32:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你检查了压板了吗? - 压板没事.\N{\fs14}- You check your planking? - Planking's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.41,1:32:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹,你认为要多久能修好?\N{\fs14}How long you figure it will take, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.64,1:32:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还不清楚.\N{\fs14}Can't tell yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.91,1:32:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会不顾质量的赶工.\N{\fs14}I won't knock off till I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.22,1:32:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么报答你呢?\N{\fs14}How am I going to pay you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.52,1:32:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去狠狠教训小日本,这就足够了.\N{\fs14}You'll fight them and I'll fix them. That's pay enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.79,1:32:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只关心能在小日本打到这来之前修好它.\N{\fs14}Only hope we get them out of here before the Japs move in.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.22,1:32:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们离这还有多远?\N{\fs14}How far away you figure they are?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.26,1:32:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就在附近岛屿那.\N{\fs14}Half the nearby islands.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.79,1:32:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,近来小日本的巡洋舰和驱逐舰成天吵个不停.\N{\fs14}Cruisers and destroyers have been nosing around for days.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.97,1:32:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们登陆了,你打算怎么办?\N{\fs14}What are you going to do if they make a landing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.84,1:32:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要跟他们决一死战.\N{\fs14}They'll have to fight to get me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.40,1:32:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你,埃斯沃多·佩雷拉!\N{\fs14}You, Ascevedo Perreira!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.47,1:32:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,离水桶远点.\N{\fs14}Get away from that water bucket.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.41,1:32:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没到时间呢.\N{\fs14}Drink on your own time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.45,1:32:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈,我想起来了,来吸一口吧?\N{\fs14}That reminds me. How about a little snort?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.78,1:32:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,晚点再说吧.\N{\fs14}Later.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.92,1:33:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,船长!\N{\fs14}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.15,1:33:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,潜艇.\N{\fs14}Submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.32,1:33:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-29潜艇来了,长官.\N{\fs14}S-29 coming up the channel, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.92,1:33:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,食品准备好了.\N{\fs14}And chow is ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.70,1:33:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉命前来装载粮食和奎宁...\N{\fs14}I have orders to load food and quinine...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.83,1:33:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,运往科雷吉多尔岛.\N{\fs14}...and try to run it to Corregidor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.73,1:33:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,总部还希望能利用汽船穿越封锁输送补给.\N{\fs14}They also want the interisland steamers to try the blockade.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.80,1:33:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这有7条小汽轮.\N{\fs14}We've got seven small steamers here.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.47,1:33:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,另外还可以再装配出一两条明轮船.\N{\fs14}We might rig up a side-wheeler or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.18,1:33:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一些汽艇.\N{\fs14}And some motored sailors.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.61,1:33:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我立刻安排补给品的事情.\N{\fs14}I'll arrange for supplies at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.78,1:33:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们快点吧.\N{\fs14}Let's give her a whirl.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.21,1:33:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有事,再见.\N{\fs14}I've got work to do. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.55,1:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,等等,斯纳菲.\N{\fs14}Oh, Snuffy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.76,1:33:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能给我们几条鱼雷吗?\N{\fs14}How about getting torpedoes from you?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.57,1:33:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,给你那些爆竹用?\N{\fs14}For those cracker boxes of yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.00,1:33:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己都不知道什么时候才能再得到补充呢.\N{\fs14}No telling when we'll see a mother ship again.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.67,1:33:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们巡逻多久了?\N{\fs14}How long you been on patrol?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.31,1:33:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,战争爆发时就开始了.\N{\fs14}Since the war started.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.74,1:34:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们都有什么战果呢?\N{\fs14}What did you get?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.88,1:34:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,两艘小型护卫舰.\N{\fs14}Two small freighters.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.31,1:34:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法,运气太差.\N{\fs14}We had hard luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.71,1:34:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在海底转悠时,这些破烂 爆竹已经击沉了2艘巡洋舰...\N{\fs14}While you've been cruising, those cracker boxes have sunk 2 cruisers...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.02,1:34:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘轻型航空母舰...\N{\fs14}...an auxiliary aircraft carrier...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.05,1:34:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一艘1万吨的油船和一艘大型护卫舰..\N{\fs14}...a 10,000-ton tanker, a large freighter...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.56,1:34:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,以及不计其数的小日本兔崽子...\N{\fs14}...a flock of barges and numerous sons of Nippon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.23,1:34:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我们的正事....\N{\fs14}And also in our brief career...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.86,1:34:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们传送了比西联还要多的的信息.\N{\fs14}...we've carried more messages than Western Union.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.06,1:34:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想帮你们,但我有命令..\N{\fs14}I'd like to help you out, but I got orders-
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.37,1:34:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}[台词如此，1932年奥斯卡奖名单并未见此片]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.37,1:34:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1932年奥斯卡获奖电影"德伯家的苔丝"\N{\fs14}Who played the leading lady in "Tess of the d'Urbevilles"...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.57,1:34:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谁演的女主角?\N{\fs14}...in 1932 at the Academy?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.48,1:34:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的艇员知道吗?\N{\fs14}And does your crew know about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.12,1:34:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想要多少?\N{\fs14}How many do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.72,1:34:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你有16条鱼雷.\N{\fs14}You've got 16.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.75,1:34:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们8条.\N{\fs14}We'll take 8.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.12,1:34:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把它们送到它们该去的地方的.\N{\fs14}And we'll try and put them where they belong.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.13,1:34:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.82,1:35:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请让一下.\N{\fs14}Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.42,1:35:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我有好消息给你.\N{\fs14}I finally have good news for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.36,1:35:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明天会有轰炸机从澳大利亚飞来...\N{\fs14}Tomorrow, bombers will take off from Australia...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.96,1:35:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,轰炸这的日本舰队.\N{\fs14}...and blast every Jap ship here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.17,1:35:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直盼着呢.\N{\fs14}We've been hoping for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.70,1:35:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有一个问题.\N{\fs14}But there's a catch in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.87,1:35:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有艘巡洋舰正向这驶来.\N{\fs14}A cruiser is headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.34,1:35:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可能还有驱逐舰跟着.\N{\fs14}Probably has destroyers with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.84,1:35:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,情报显示那是"最上"级重巡洋舰.\N{\fs14}Information says she's of the Mogami class.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.95,1:35:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明白那对你们意味着什么吗?\N{\fs14}Does that mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.51,1:35:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,十分清楚,长官.\N{\fs14}That's about as big as they come. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.82,1:35:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你们去阻止他们,否则..\N{\fs14}She'll shell these food ships before they get away from the dock.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.19,1:35:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的运送粮食的船队还没离港就会被消灭.\N{\fs14}Unless you boys can stop her.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.63,1:35:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能办到吗?\N{\fs14}Can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.26,1:36:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们试试.长官. -很好.\N{\fs14}- Can try, sir. - That's fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.60,1:36:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快去准备吧,用我的车子.祝你们好运.\N{\fs14}Better get going. Take my driver and good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.87,1:36:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我来开车.\N{\fs14}I'll drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.82,1:36:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"最上"级巡洋舰,什么感想,莱恩?\N{\fs14}Mogami-class cruiser mean anything to you, Mr. Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.77,1:36:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么情况,头? -有什么消息,布里克?\N{\fs14}- What's up, Skipper? - Any news, Brick?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.34,1:36:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹,还要多久能修好?\N{\fs14}How soon can you get them ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.27,1:36:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不超过3天.\N{\fs14}Not for three days, with the 35 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.71,1:36:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还得加快进度. -那些轴承很费时间的\N{\fs14}- You can go quicker than that. - Them bearings take time!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.41,1:36:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌的艇好了,但是艇身需要先泡24小时.\N{\fs14}Rusty's boat's ready, but her hull ought to soak 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.62,1:36:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那...41号艇只好单独出击了.\N{\fs14}The 41 boat will have to go alone, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.78,1:36:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把41号艇准备好.\N{\fs14}Get her ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.69,1:36:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的,小伙子们,来吧.\N{\fs14}All right, gang, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.13,1:37:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩先生,这太过分了.\N{\fs14}This has gone far enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.23,1:37:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么好事总被41号艇抢了?\N{\fs14}That 41 boat is always hogging the good jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.60,1:37:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,浸泡艇身这事,我们可以在路上完成啊.\N{\fs14}We'll soak on our way to hit the Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.23,1:37:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们干啥?坐这干等他们回来?\N{\fs14}What do we do? Sit on our duffs until they get back?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.47,1:37:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,单凭41号艇很难完成任务的.\N{\fs14}The 41 can't handle this job alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.38,1:37:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样,长官?\N{\fs14}How about it, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.15,1:37:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧.可是,万一它开始进水的话...\N{\fs14}But if she starts taking water...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.18,1:37:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...必须立即返航.\N{\fs14}...turn back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.01,1:37:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,准备完毕.\N{\fs14}Ready here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.77,1:38:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,埃斯佩朗莎,它下水了.\N{\fs14}There she goes, Esperanzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.50,1:38:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就像水过猫背般滑顺.\N{\fs14}Like water off a cat's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.51,1:38:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿,拉斯悌!\N{\fs14}Rusty!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.28,1:38:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喝酒的,但我要痛饮庆祝.\N{\fs14}I ain't a drinking man.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.71,1:38:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我会把大部分留到你们回来再喝的.\N{\fs14}But I'm saving most of this till you get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.41,1:39:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在那!乖乖,它在那!\N{\fs14}There she is! Jumping Jeremiah, there she is!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.08,1:39:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌注意了.\N{\fs14}Rusty from Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.69,1:39:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我从滩头那边发起攻击,你从海上进攻.\N{\fs14}I'll make my run from the beach. You make yours from seaward.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.36,1:39:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,完毕.\N{\fs14}Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.96,1:39:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是拉斯悌.\N{\fs14}Brick from Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.33,1:39:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,收到命令.\N{\fs14}Wilco.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.76,1:39:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,预备!\N{\fs14}Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.72,1:40:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire one!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.85,1:40:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,二号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire two!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.61,1:40:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯悌准备.\N{\fs14}Rusty from Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.18,1:40:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,开始攻击.\N{\fs14}Start your run.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.78,1:40:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,开始攻击,完毕.\N{\fs14}Start your run. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.42,1:40:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是拉斯悌,收到.\N{\fs14}Brick from Rusty. Wilco.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.39,1:40:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,出击!\N{\fs14}Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.69,1:41:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,预备!\N{\fs14}Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.00,1:41:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire one!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.34,1:41:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,二号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire two!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.14,1:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好鱼雷!\N{\fs14}Stand by your torpedoes!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.32,1:42:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-就绪. -3号发射!\N{\fs14}- One! - Fire three!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.99,1:42:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-4号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire four!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.79,1:43:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼雷准备!\N{\fs14}Stand by torpedoes!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.63,1:43:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来点漂亮的!\N{\fs14}Let's make these good!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.08,1:43:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,准备.\N{\fs14}Yards.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.32,1:43:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,3号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire three!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.22,1:43:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,4号发射!\N{\fs14}Fire four!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.36,1:43:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走!\N{\fs14}Let's drag our tails out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.86,1:44:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们看不到我们长官,这岛挡着呢.\N{\fs14}We're lee of the land, sir. They've lost us.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.50,1:44:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你来.\N{\fs14}Take over.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.27,1:44:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克他们应该有机会跑掉的,是吧长官?\N{\fs14}Think Mr. Brickley had a chance to get away, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.97,1:44:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他总能跑掉的.\N{\fs14}He usually does.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.89,1:45:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,机枪要没弹药了.\N{\fs14}Running low on 50-caliber!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.86,1:45:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-火势失去控制了! -抓住马汉!\N{\fs14}- We can't control the fire! - Grab Mahan!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.32,1:46:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,隐蔽!\N{\fs14}Take cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.57,1:47:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,比分多少?\N{\fs14}What's the score?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.00,1:47:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,刚第一局,孩子.\N{\fs14}Ninth inning, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.51,1:47:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉,神父不在.\N{\fs14}I'm sorry. The father is not here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.34,1:47:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他在医院呆了2天了.\N{\fs14}He has been at the hospital for two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.30,1:48:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,军人死后应当有葬礼.\N{\fs14}A serviceman is supposed to have a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.14,1:48:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是对他为国捐躯的一种肯定.\N{\fs14}That's a tribute to the way he spent his life.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.58,1:48:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抬棺...\N{\fs14}Escort...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.45,1:48:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,鸣枪....\N{\fs14}...firing squad...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.52,1:48:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,身覆国旗...\N{\fs14}...wrapped in the flag he served under...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.79,1:48:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他应享有的.\N{\fs14}...and died for.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.03,1:48:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但战争时期,只能舍弃这些奢望...\N{\fs14}In war you got to forget those things...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.97,1:48:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,按我们能够办到的最好的方式下葬.\N{\fs14}...and get buried the best way you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.34,1:48:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都知道...\N{\fs14}You all knew...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.44,1:48:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,德国佬拉森,还有施拉格 马汉.\N{\fs14}...Squarehead Larsen and Slug Mahan.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.58,1:49:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是一对好水兵.\N{\fs14}They were just a couple of bluejackets who did their job.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.08,1:49:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尽职尽责.\N{\fs14}Did it well.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.28,1:49:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,34号艇不能没有他们.\N{\fs14}34 boat couldn't have got along without them.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.46,1:49:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,德国佬 拉森.\N{\fs14}Squarehead Larsen.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.03,1:49:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他是海军最好的厨师.\N{\fs14}He's the best cook in the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.80,1:49:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他最爱亚力桑那号.\N{\fs14}He loved the old Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.07,1:49:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们都去了.\N{\fs14}Now they're both gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.60,1:49:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,施拉格....\N{\fs14}Slug...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:28.61,1:49:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是...\N{\fs14}...he was always...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.71,1:49:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...吟诗\N{\fs14}...quoting verse.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.75,1:49:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...弄曲.\N{\fs14}Bits of poetry.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.02,1:49:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...所以\N{\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.65,1:49:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在给他献上一首诗.\N{\fs14}...here's one for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:44.62,1:49:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一熟悉的一首.\N{\fs14}It's about the only one I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.53,1:49:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在广阔的...\N{\fs14}Under the wide...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.33,1:49:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,星空之下\N{\fs14}...starry sky
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.03,1:49:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,掘好墓穴\N{\fs14}Dig the grave
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.10,1:49:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让我安眠.\N{\fs14}And let me lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.83,1:49:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,开心的活着\N{\fs14}Glad did I live
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.47,1:50:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,无悔的逝去\N{\fs14}And gladly die
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.21,1:50:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一个愿望\N{\fs14}And I laid me down with a will
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.48,1:50:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在我的墓碑上刻下:\N{\fs14}This be the verse you grave for me
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.18,1:50:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他安眠在他长久向往的地方\N{\fs14}Here he lies where he longed to be
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.35,1:50:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大海...\N{\fs14}Home is the sailor...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:20.19,1:50:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她是水手的家\N{\fs14}...home from the sea
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.56,1:50:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就如山岗是猎人的家.\N{\fs14}And the hunter home from the hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.94,1:50:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗,长官?\N{\fs14}Is it all right, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.17,1:50:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯.\N{\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.85,1:51:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你,孩子.\N{\fs14}Thank you, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.69,1:51:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起.酒吧关闭了.\N{\fs14}Sorry. Bar closed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.19,1:51:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们要走了! -不,酒吧没关门.\N{\fs14}- We go away! - Sorry, bar is open.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.12,1:51:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不,不!日本人来了,日本人就要打来了!\N{\fs14}No, no! Jap come, Jap come!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.15,1:51:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐!\N{\fs14}Musica, Se駉r Teniente.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.38,1:51:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐.Es 圣·弗朗西斯科\N{\fs14}Musica. Es San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.44,1:52:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是WBKR 圣·弗朗西斯科.\N{\fs14}WBKR San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.97,1:52:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下.\N{\fs14}A brief interruption, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.84,1:52:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,下面播报来自菲律宾的不幸消息.\N{\fs14}This is spot and tragic news from the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.78,1:52:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,经过艰苦血战之后...\N{\fs14}The white flag of surrender was hoisted...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.61,1:53:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午巴丹堡垒升起了白旗.\N{\fs14}...on the bloody heights of Bataan this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.32,1:53:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,3万6千名美国士兵...\N{\fs14}36,000 United States soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.22,1:53:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他们饥渴疲惫...\N{\fs14}...hungry...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.42,1:53:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,衣衫褴褛....\N{\fs14}...ragged, half-starved shadows...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.12,1:53:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,身陷绝境拼死奋战...\N{\fs14}...trapped like rats but dying like men...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.99,1:53:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,终被2万日军精锐部队击败.\N{\fs14}...were finally worn down by 200,000 picked Japanese troops.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.57,1:53:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们为不可动摇的信念战斗...\N{\fs14}Men who fight for an unshakable faith...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.34,1:53:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,超乎常人.\N{\fs14}...are more than flesh.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.24,1:53:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然而他们毕竟是血肉之躯,\N{\fs14}But they're not steel.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:22.77,1:53:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,生命终会凋零.\N{\fs14}Flesh must yield at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.38,1:53:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,承受超过极限时,\N{\fs14}Endurance melts away.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.71,1:53:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,结局就不可避免.\N{\fs14}The end must come.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.05,1:53:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,巴丹虽然沦陷了.\N{\fs14}Bataan has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.78,1:53:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是巴丹守军那激励了...\N{\fs14}But the spirit that made it a beacon...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.12,1:53:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所有爱好自由的人民的精神永远不会消退.\N{\fs14}...to all lovers of liberty will never falter.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.79,1:53:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在日军猛烈炮击科雷吉多尔...\N{\fs14}The white flag was hardly hoisted over Bataan...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.16,1:53:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在菲律宾最后的据点后,\N{\fs14}...before Jap artillery began slamming away at Corregidor...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.16,1:53:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,巴丹半岛终于升起了白旗.\N{\fs14}...our last strong point in the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.72,1:54:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们,布里克雷牺牲了...\N{\fs14}Men, with Mr. Brickley gone...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.38,1:54:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我将继续做他会做的事.\N{\fs14}...I'll carry on the way I think he would.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.59,1:54:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意你关于莱特岛的观点.\N{\fs14}I think you're right about Leyte Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.49,1:54:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那边有陆军的人.或许我们能坚守到援军到来.\N{\fs14}There's Army men over there. Maybe we can hold out till help comes.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.86,1:54:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,全力守住每一个桥头和隘口,拉弗悌.\N{\fs14}Dig in at every bridgehead and pass, Lefty.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.59,1:54:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让小日本崽子付出代价.\N{\fs14}Make them pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.60,1:54:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你们好运. -再见.\N{\fs14}- Good luck, fellas. - So long.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.77,1:55:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,重复命令.\N{\fs14}Repeat your orders.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.37,1:55:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,找到马丁将军,向他报告并保护他.\N{\fs14}To find and report to General Martin and keep him up to date.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.98,1:55:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,出发吧.\N{\fs14}All right, get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.21,1:55:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨,你好.小伙子. -你好,长官.\N{\fs14}- Old Franklin High, Junior. - Roosevelt High, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.09,1:55:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹,我要去找布里克.\N{\fs14}Dad, I'm going to try and find Brick.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.92,1:55:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不跟我们一起走呢?\N{\fs14}Why don't you come along with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.26,1:55:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这干了40年了,孩子.\N{\fs14}I've worked 40 years for this, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.80,1:55:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是死也要战死在这.\N{\fs14}If I leave it, they'll have to carry me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.41,1:57:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨,小伙子.\N{\fs14}Hello, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.72,1:57:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都以为日本人打中你们了.\N{\fs14}We thought the Japs got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.28,1:57:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也一位他们打中你们了.\N{\fs14}I thought they got you too.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.72,1:57:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了?\N{\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:32.12,1:57:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们往南走的时候搁浅了.\N{\fs14}Ran south through shallow water.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.20,1:57:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人呢?\N{\fs14}Where's your crew?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.37,1:57:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,马汉 和拉森牺牲了.\N{\fs14}We lost Mahan and Larsen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.40,1:57:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-还有几个受了伤. -他们怎么打中施拉格的?\N{\fs14}- Couple of the kids got hurt. - How'd they get Slug?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.44,1:57:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机上的机枪打的.\N{\fs14}Machine gun from a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.08,1:57:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真不幸.\N{\fs14}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:59.25,1:58:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴您回来.\N{\fs14}Glad to see you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.50,1:58:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的船呢?\N{\fs14}Where's your boat?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:18.00,1:58:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被日本飞机的炸弹击中.\N{\fs14}Jap bombers got her.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.67,1:58:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把船烧了.\N{\fs14}We burned the 35 boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.51,1:58:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,艇员往莱特岛去了\N{\fs14}The gang headed for Leyte.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.28,1:58:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,它闯过来了.\N{\fs14}She's through.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.48,1:58:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马丁将军把她转给了陆军...\N{\fs14}General Martin turned her over to the Army...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.85,1:58:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,去拉瑙湖执行任务.\N{\fs14}...to run errands on Lake Lanao.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.92,1:58:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,海军兄弟.我们接管了.\N{\fs14}Okay, Navy. We're taking over.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.84,1:59:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧,陆军们,把她带走吧.\N{\fs14}Okay, Army. Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.79,1:59:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好了,鼓起劲,我们要出发了.\N{\fs14}All right, gather up your gear. We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:57.37,1:59:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-你也在找亚利桑那号吗? -没错.\N{\fs14}You looking for the Arizona too?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.15,2:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷.\N{\fs14}Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.29,2:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-我受命载你和莱恩先生飞去澳大利亚. -澳大利亚?\N{\fs14}I have orders to fly you and Ryan to Australia.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.76,2:02:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对,还有准尉加德纳和克洛斯.\N{\fs14}Also ensigns Gardner and Cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.29,2:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们在镇西面. -我们会找到他们.\N{\fs14}- They're west of town. - We'll find them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:39.53,2:02:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要我们去?我们只是上尉而已.\N{\fs14}Why us? We're just a couple of lieutenants.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.43,2:02:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们证明了PT快艇在战争中的价值.\N{\fs14}You men have proved that PT boats have some value in this war.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:46.00,2:02:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,华府希望你们能参与建设这支部队.\N{\fs14}Washington wants you in the States to build them up.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.74,2:02:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这是命令.\N{\fs14}Those are my orders.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.21,2:02:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人呢?\N{\fs14}And the men?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.34,2:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没地方了.\N{\fs14}There isn't room.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.78,2:02:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-可是马丁将军,这些人... -飞机上没有地方了,布里克雷.\N{\fs14}- General Martin, those men- - There isn't room for them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.98,2:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-桥准备好了,长官. -炸吧.\N{\fs14}- Bridge ready, sir. - Let her go.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.72,2:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们犯了个错误..\N{\fs14}I think we're making a mistake-
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.59,2:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机上没位置了!布里克雷. 即刻去机场报到.\N{\fs14}There isn't room. Report to the airport right away.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.46,2:03:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,开车. 你最好赶紧去.\N{\fs14}Driver. And you better get going.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:25.14,2:03:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,事情总不能如我们所愿\N{\fs14}Makes a fine pair of heels out of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.86,2:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我和莱恩先生接到命令要撤回国内.\N{\fs14}Mr. Ryan and I have been ordered out.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.35,2:04:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运,长官.\N{\fs14}Good luck, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:12.79,2:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,也祝你好运,钟斯.\N{\fs14}Good luck to you, Jonesy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.69,2:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也祝你好运.\N{\fs14}That goes for you too.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.86,2:04:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,照顾好他.\N{\fs14}Watch him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.24,2:04:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,长官,我想和你握个手.\N{\fs14}I'd like to shake your hand.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.74,2:04:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸.\N{\fs14}That'll be a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.77,2:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,纵有千言万语,我只想说...\N{\fs14}The book doesn't mean much out here, so I'm going to say...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:35.04,2:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都很优秀....再见,布里克雷.\N{\fs14}...so long, Brick. You've been a swell guy.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.25,2:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,艾瑞斯.\N{\fs14}So long, Irish.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:40.85,2:04:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,拉斯悌>\N{\fs14}So long, Rusty.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:42.65,2:04:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,迈克尔.\N{\fs14}So long, you big mick.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.59,2:04:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,帆缆军士长的助手莫加西.\N{\fs14}Chief Boatswain's Mate Mulcahey.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.96,2:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-你接替指挥. -是,长官.\N{\fs14}Take over.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:59.27,2:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,向--右--转!\N{\fs14}Right face!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.84,2:05:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,交叉步,跟我来!\N{\fs14}Cross step. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.56,2:05:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-第四陆战旅. -41号.\N{\fs14}- Fourth Marines. - Forty-one.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.06,2:06:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.23,2:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 斯仲格中尉. - 39号.\N{\fs14}- Lieutenant Strong. - Thirty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.03,2:06:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的.\N{\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.74,2:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给. - 谢谢,长官.\N{\fs14}- Here you are. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.31,2:06:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷,美国海军.\N{\fs14}Brickley, U.S.N.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:12.68,2:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,27号.\N{\fs14}Number 27.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.11,2:06:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莱恩,美国海军.\N{\fs14}Ryan, U.S.N.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:18.58,2:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,28号.\N{\fs14}Number 28.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.25,2:06:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起,我不知道上面有没有我的名字.\N{\fs14}I'm sorry. I don't know if my name's on that list.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.12,2:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是詹姆斯·莫顿少校.\N{\fs14}Morton. Major James Morton.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.06,2:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,31号,上校.\N{\fs14}You're number 31, Major.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.23,2:06:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我能走吗?\N{\fs14}I get to go?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.33,2:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,每架飞机搭30个人.\N{\fs14}Each plane holds 30 men.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.83,2:06:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果来两架,您就能走.\N{\fs14}If two planes come, you'll get to go.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.37,2:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,31号,谢谢.\N{\fs14}31. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.94,2:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望那些人会出现.\N{\fs14}Wish those kids would show up.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.88,2:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,##哎,Ohio!\N{\fs14}Ohio!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.91,2:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨,拉斯悌,你好吗?\N{\fs14}Hi, Rusty. How are you, fella?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.88,2:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候离开科雷吉多尔的?\N{\fs14}When did you leave The Rock?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:53.52,2:06:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,四五天前,或者有一周了吧.我也记不清了.\N{\fs14}Four or five days ago, a week. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.92,2:07:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得桑蒂吗?那个蓝眼睛的小护士.\N{\fs14}Remember Sandy, the little nurse with the green eyes?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.03,2:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-记得. -其他11,000人也记得.\N{\fs14}Sure. So will 11,000 other guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.50,2:07:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道她现在在哪吗?\N{\fs14}You know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.20,2:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不,我不知道.\N{\fs14}No, I don't know where she'd be now.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.47,2:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能逃出来在山里...\N{\fs14}She might be out in the hills...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.47,2:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,或者在某个监狱里.\N{\fs14}...or a prisoner somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.37,2:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,刷洗碟子.\N{\fs14}Swell dish.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.21,2:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜她对你要比对其他人重要的多.\N{\fs14}I guess she meant more to you than she did the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.92,2:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的希望她没事.\N{\fs14}I sure hope she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.52,2:07:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后一次和她说话..\N{\fs14}Last time I talked to her...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.22,2:07:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是在巴丹的电话里.\N{\fs14}...was over the telephone on Bataan.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.79,2:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,声音还是那么动听.\N{\fs14}Voice sounded swell.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.56,2:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那么清晰...\N{\fs14}Clear...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.73,2:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,..勇敢...\N{\fs14}...and brave...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.33,2:07:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那么遥远.\N{\fs14}...and far away.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.11,2:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一架飞机.\N{\fs14}Only one plane.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.55,2:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,加德纳和克洛斯到底去哪了呢?\N{\fs14}Where do you suppose Gardner and Cross could have gotten to?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.54,2:08:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以上人了,上尉.\N{\fs14}Quite a load, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.77,2:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨,斯莫基! -嗨,乔.\N{\fs14}- Hey, Smokey! - Hey, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.24,2:08:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喊到名字的,请登机.\N{\fs14}As I call your names, kindly step into the plane.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.61,2:08:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,1号,T.V.史密斯中士.\N{\fs14}Number one, Sergeant T.V. Smith.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.02,2:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,2号,A.C.詹姆斯中尉.\N{\fs14}Number two, Lieutenant A. C. James.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:41.12,2:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,立正!\N{\fs14}Attention!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.70,2:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,布里克雷.\N{\fs14}Brickley.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.70,2:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,见到将军时,告诉他这就要失陷了.\N{\fs14}When you see the General, tell him the end here is near.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.38,2:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他问你我想要什么...\N{\fs14}If he should ask you what we want...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.14,2:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他,我想要一只海军特遣舰队...\N{\fs14}...tell him a Navy task force...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:04.25,2:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,满载汽油的油船和十万人.\N{\fs14}...a tanker loaded with gasoline and 100,000 men.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:07.65,2:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有这些,我们就能收复失陷的岛屿.\N{\fs14}Give me that, and we can start taking the islands back.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.85,2:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他不可能得到这么多,但是 如果他问起来,你就这么跟他说.\N{\fs14}I know he probably hasn't got them, but if he asks you, tell him.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.09,2:09:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是,长官.找到加德纳和克洛斯了吗?\N{\fs14}Yes, sir. Have they located Gardner and Cross?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:17.83,2:09:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没有,还在找.\N{\fs14}No, they're still looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:26.34,2:09:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,27号,海军上尉布里克雷先生.\N{\fs14}Number 27, Lieutenant Brickley, Navy.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.54,2:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,28号,海军上尉莱恩先生.\N{\fs14}Number 28, Lieutenant Ryan, Navy.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:34.98,2:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,29号,加德纳准尉.\N{\fs14}Number 29, Ensign Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.25,2:09:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,30号,克洛斯准尉.\N{\fs14}Number 30, Ensign Cross.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.43,2:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,31号,詹姆斯·莫顿少校.\N{\fs14}Thirty-one, Major James Morton.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.86,2:09:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,到.\N{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.03,2:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,32号,卡特上尉.\N{\fs14}Number 32, Captain Carter.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.10,2:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,到.-\N{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.80,2:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,齐了.\N{\fs14}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.91,2:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再见,中士.\N{\fs14}So long, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.87,2:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,莫顿少校,卡特上尉,很抱歉.\N{\fs14}Major Morton and Captain Carter, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.61,2:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的位置是留给那两人人的.\N{\fs14}Your places are assigned to these two men. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.58,2:10:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对不起我们迟到了,长官.我们遇到炮击. -我们的车子坏了\N{\fs14}- Sorry we're late, but we got strafed. - We both lost our bikes.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.12,2:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 实在抱歉,长官. - 没关系.\N{\fs14}- I'm sorry, sir. - Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.79,2:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-祝你们好运,水兵. -祝你们一路顺风.\N{\fs14}- Good luck, sailor. - I hope you have a smooth trip home.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.72,2:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你活着,能帮忙给我太太捎个口信吗?\N{\fs14}If you get through, would you mail a note to my wife?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.43,2:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,当然.\N{\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.83,2:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是她的电话,给她打个长途电话.\N{\fs14}Here's her phone number. Call her long-distance.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.76,2:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她你见过我,我永远爱她.\N{\fs14}Tell her you saw me and that I still love her.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.20,2:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定会的.\N{\fs14}You bet I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.57,2:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,记住了,水兵.\N{\fs14}Make no passes at her, sailor.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.90,2:11:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-一路顺风! -等等.\N{\fs14}- Happy landings! - Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.77,2:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己给她打电话吧, 我在这还有点事.\N{\fs14}You phone her. I got business here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:11.91,2:11:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你要回国办你的事.让开.\N{\fs14}You got business back in the States. Gangway.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.55,2:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你为谁战斗,布里克雷?\N{\fs14}Who are you working for?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:19.52,2:11:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为你自己吗?\N{\fs14}Yourself?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.28,2:11:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的对,兄弟.\N{\fs14}He said it, fella.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.20,2:11:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢.\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.20,2:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气.\N{\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.02,2:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还有飞机来吗?\N{\fs14}How many more planes are coming in?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.65,2:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再有了.\N{\fs14}None.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.89,2:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子...\N{\fs14}Look, son...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.29,2:12:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回国是有任务的.\N{\fs14}...we're going home to do a job.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:05.36,2:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是--为打回来作好准备.\N{\fs14}And that job is to get ready to come back.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:10.00,2:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-- 明白了吗? -- 明白.\N{\fs14}Check?  Check
